Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你岂不曾听过吗\N{\fs55}Have you not heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,永在的耶和华 创造地极的主\N{\fs55}The Lord is the everlasting God, the Creator of the ends of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,从不疲乏 也不困倦\N{\fs55}He will not grow tired or weary,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他的智慧无法测度\N{\fs55}and His understanding no one can fathom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,疲乏者 他赐能力 软弱者 他加力量\N{\fs55}He gives strength to the weary and increases the power of the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,即使少年 也会疲乏困倦 也会绊住跌倒\N{\fs55}Even youths grow tired and weary, and young men stumble and fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但仰望上帝者 必将重新得力\N{\fs55}But those who hope in the Lord will renew their strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们必如鹰展翅上腾\N{\fs55}They will soar on wings like eagles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们可奔跑而不困倦\N{\fs55}They will run and not grow weary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们将行走却不疲乏\N{\fs55}They will walk and not be faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,戴斯蒙 挺住\N{\fs55}Desmond, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,挺住啊 戴斯蒙\N{\fs55}Hang on, Desmond!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会带你离开这里的\N{\fs55}We're going to get you out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\fs85\bord0\shad0\c&HF3FDEF&\pos(550,919.232)}蓝脊山  弗吉尼亚州
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\fs85\bord0\shad0\c&HF3FDEF&\pos(442.8,912.816)}十六年前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,戴斯蒙\N{\fs55}Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,戴斯蒙\N{\fs55}Desmond!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么\N{\fs55}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等等我 - 快跟上\N{\fs55}- Wait up. - Catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我有话要跟你说\N{\fs55}Wait up, I've got something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事 哈尔\N{\fs55}What, Hal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,比赛谁先登顶吧\N{\fs55}Race you to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你耍赖\N{\fs55}Hey! Cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,回头见了 小短腿\N{\fs55}See you later,slowpoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 需要拉你一把吗 - 我没事\N{\fs55}- Want a hand? - I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 下去吧 - 蠢货\N{\fs55}- Sit down! - Ah,you dope!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别闹了 - 你别闹了\N{\fs55}- Quit it. - You quit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊\N{\fs55}For Pete's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,快从岩脊上下来 俩倒霉孩子\N{\fs55}Hey! Get away from that ledge,you damn fool kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,小心摔断脖子\N{\fs55}You're going to break your necks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,道斯家的孩子 跟他们老爸一样疯\N{\fs55}It's them Doss kids. Crazy as their old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在杰森路和主街交口挖出一块地\N{\fs55}They dug up the corner of Jackson and Main...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,铺上了人行道\N{\fs55}Putting in a sidewalk...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你们肯定认不出那里了\N{\fs55}You boys wouldn't recognize it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,估计他们也认不出你们了\N{\fs55}Mind you,I doubt they'd recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我路过时 他们连我都不认识了\N{\fs55}They hardly know me when I walk by 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:04:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像我也一起死了\N{\fs55}It's like I died with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像我们从没存在过\N{\fs55}It's like we boys never existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就跟你们说这些了\N{\fs55}Well,that's all I got for you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,用右臂挡住他 戴斯蒙\N{\fs55}Block him with your right,Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,别打了 听见了吗\N{\fs55}Stop it! Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.60,0:05:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们怎么打起来了 - 他们打架从来不需要理由\N{\fs55}- What are they fighting about? - When'd they ever need a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆 拜托\N{\fs55}Tom! Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,别拦着他们 省得我抽他们俩\N{\fs55}Why stop 'em? Saves me whipping them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,现在这样 我抽赢的人就行了\N{\fs55}This way,I just whip the one that wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆\N{\fs55}Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fs55}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs55}Oh,God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆\N{\fs55}Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,快醒醒 能听见吗\N{\fs55}Wake up,can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你都干了什么\N{\fs55}What the hell have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他没反应了\N{\fs55}He can't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我去拿些冰块\N{\fs55}I'll get some ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把那篮子拿走 - 好的\N{\fs55}- You shift that basket. - I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他还有呼吸吗\N{\fs55}Is he breathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔 你能听见吗\N{\fs55}Hal? Hal,can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔 你能听见吗\N{\fs55}Hal,can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔 快醒醒\N{\fs55}Hal... Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他的瞳孔扩大了\N{\fs55}He's dilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔\N{\fs55}Hal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道自己做了什么吗\N{\fs55}What do you think you're doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我得揍你了 你知道规矩的\N{\fs55}I'm gonna have to beat you now, you know the rules.
