Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你听见了吗 戴斯蒙\N{\fs55}You hear me,Desmond?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 戴斯蒙 - 汤姆 别说了\N{\fs55}- Desmond! - Tom,stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你揍他一顿 能让他学到什么\N{\fs55}What's that gonna teach the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经够暴力了\N{\fs55}He's violent enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧 你继续宠着他吧\N{\fs55}Okay,fine, you go smother him in kisses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你来告诉他 这世界都是温柔美好的\N{\fs55}You tell him the world's a soft and gentle place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔会没事的\N{\fs55}Hal's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我差点害死他 - 是啊\N{\fs55}- I could have killed him. - Yes,you could have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,杀人是最严重的罪恶\N{\fs55}Murder,it's the worst sin of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,夺走别人的性命\N{\fs55}And to take another man's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在上帝眼中 是最恶劣的罪行\N{\fs55}that is the most egregious sin in the Lord's sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也是最让上帝难过了\N{\fs55}Nothing hurts his heart so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你听不懂人话吗\N{\fs55}Don't you understand English?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我得再跟你说一遍吗\N{\fs55}Do I have to tell you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我让开 否则别怪我动手了\N{\fs55}You move,woman, or I will wallop you good and hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,大晚上吵什么 你还好吗 Bertha\N{\fs55}What the hell's going on? You okay,Bertha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,少管闲事\N{\fs55}You mind your own damned business!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,去睡觉吧 汤姆\N{\fs55}Go sleep it off,Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨他\N{\fs55}I hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\fs55}Momma?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么如此讨厌我们\N{\fs55}Why does he hate us so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是讨厌我们\N{\fs55}Oh,he don't hate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候 他是在恨自己\N{\fs55}He hates himself sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸其实不是这样的\N{\fs55}Your daddy tonight, that ain't the real him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望你能知道 战争之前 他有多好\N{\fs55}I wish you knew him like I did,before the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们唱得怎么样 戴斯蒙\N{\fs55}How'd we sound,Desmond?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如同天使一般 妈妈\N{\fs55}Like a heavenly host of angels,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道说谎也是罪恶的 尤其在教堂里\N{\fs55}Now,you know it's a sin to tell a lie, especially in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没说是会唱歌的天使\N{\fs55}Well,I ain't never said they were singing angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,外面怎么了 戴斯蒙\N{\fs55}What's going on out there? Desmond!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:10:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快抬起来\N{\fs55}Get it up,get it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,把他拖出来 拖帆布就好\N{\fs55}Drag him out. Just the tarp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我来叫救护车\N{\fs55}I'll phone an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,来不及了 用Joshua的卡车\N{\fs55}No,no time. Joshua's pickup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快点 - 好的\N{\fs55}- Quick! - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你会没事的 不会有事的\N{\fs55}You're going to be fine now. You're going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这里都是好医生\N{\fs55}You're in good hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况\N{\fs55}What have we got here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,动脉割伤 拿缝合工具来\N{\fs55}It's a severed artery. Get some sutures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 医生\N{\fs55}Yes,doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,按住这里 是你绑的止血带吗\N{\fs55}Put some pressure on it. Did you apply this tourniquet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 干得好\N{\fs55}- Yes,sir. - Nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你 也许他就没命了\N{\fs55}You might have saved this boy's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,能听见吗 你会没事的\N{\fs55}You staying with us? You're going to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字 孩子\N{\fs55}What's your name,son?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,吉尔伯特\N{\fs55}Gilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 手术吗 - 是的\N{\fs55}- Surgery? - Yeah,surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住 你会没事的\N{\fs55}Stay with us,you're gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉疼吗\N{\fs55}You feel pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住 好吗\N{\fs55}Stay with us,okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,入伍体检在那边 这里是献血室\N{\fs55}Army physicals that way. This is for giving blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fs55}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是我的血 我没事的 谢谢关心\N{\fs55}Oh,no,that's not mine. I'm fine. Thank you for asking though,ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要什么吗\N{\fs55}What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的腰带\N{\fs55}My belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我把他借给出事故的男孩了\N{\fs55}I lent it to the boy who had the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没有腰带 我的裤子总是往下掉\N{\fs55}My pants don't hold up so good without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没有你的腰带\N{\fs55}Well,uh,I don't have your belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的 腰带还在外面呢\N{\fs55}No,I know that,ma'am. It's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还在那男孩的腿上呢\N{\fs55}It's right out there with the boy still.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我还要采血\N{\fs55}Okay. I'm just here to take blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也要献血\N{\fs55}I'll give mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你去那间屋 跟其他人一起等吧\N{\fs55}Okay,go to that room over there and wait with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我一会叫你\N{\fs55}I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的房间\N{\fs55}That room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前献过血吗 该怎么称呼你\N{\fs55}You ever given blood before,Mr...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我姓道斯\N{\fs55}Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我的朋友都叫我戴斯蒙 我这是第一次献血\N{\fs55}But my friends call me Desmond. No,ma'am,this is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\c&H898E51&\frz344.1\pos(876.8,643.06)}北美珍稀鸟类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直梦想做医生的 但我没怎么上过学\N{\fs55}I always dreamed about being a doctor. But,uh,I didn't get much school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,献血以后 你可能会有点晕\N{\fs55}You may be a little dizzy when we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有人来接你吗\N{\fs55}Is somebody picking you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没有的 我走回去\N{\fs55}No,ma'am. Walking back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你住在哪呀\N{\fs55}Where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,希尔堡 女士\N{\fs55}Fort Hill,ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那还挺远呀\N{\fs55}That's a ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,五六英里吧 但我会抄林间小路的\N{\fs55}No. Just five or six miles, but I cut through the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那样是七英里\N{\fs55}It's seven that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你很喜欢树林啊\N{\fs55}You must really like the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 女士 当然了\N{\fs55}Yes,ma'am. I sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 按住这里\N{\fs55}Okay,put some pressure here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧 - 是的\N{\fs55}- You okay? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜\N{\fs55}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪呀 打扮得这么帅气\N{\fs55}Where you going looking all spruced and nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天认识一位医院的护士\N{\fs55}Met someone yesterday. A nurse over at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫桃乐茜·舒特 我要娶她\N{\fs55}Her name's Dorothy Schutte. I'm gonna marry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 她知道吗\N{\fs55}Goodness. Does she know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还不知道 不过快知道了\N{\fs55}Well,not yet. She's about to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟女人说过话吗 除了你妈妈\N{\fs55}You ever even spoken to a woman? I mean,one that's not family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,跟她说过\N{\fs55}Spoke to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,既然这样 快过来让哥抱抱\N{\fs55}Well,in that case, come give your brother a big hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 哈尔- 快过来\N{\fs55}- Hal! - Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,别用你的脏手碰我\N{\fs55}Keep your greasy paws off of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,祝我好运 妈妈\N{\fs55}Wish me luck,Momma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运啦\N{\fs55}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,下一位\N{\fs55}Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下吧 以前献过血吗\N{\fs55}Grab a seat. You ever given blood before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 女士\N{\fs55}Yes,ma'am. I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你是腰带先生\N{\fs55}You're the belt man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我是戴斯蒙\N{\fs55}Desmond,yes,ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,戴斯蒙 不能连着两天献血\N{\fs55}Well,Desmond,we can't take your blood two days in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 我是来要回我的血\N{\fs55}Well,that's good. I came to get mine back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么 - 我要把我的血拿回来\N{\fs55}- You what? - My blood. I need it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,献血不是这样的 我们不能还给你\N{\fs55}Well,it don't work like that, we can't just give it back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须还给我\N{\fs55}Well,you got to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,自从被你扎了一针\N{\fs55}Ever since you stuck me with that needle,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我的心脏就跳得特别快\N{\fs55}my heart's been beating real fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,每次想起你 心跳就更快了\N{\fs55}Every time I think about you, it beats faster still.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次被这样搭讪 太老套了\N{\fs55}I never heard that one before. It's pretty corny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs55}It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,太丢人了 我练了一个晚上呢\N{\fs55}That's a shame, I done practiced that all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还不够好吗\N{\fs55}No good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没这么说\N{\fs55}I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,动脉和静脉有什么区别\N{\fs55}What's the difference between an artery and a vein?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.16,0:16:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在说什么 - 那男孩的事故\N{\fs55}- What are you talking about? - The boy's accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,动脉会喷血\N{\fs55}Arteries spurt blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那静脉呢\N{\fs55}And veins?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,静脉是流血\N{\fs55}Bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得 你得先练练\N{\fs55}I think you need to practice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如何跟女生聊天 再出来约会\N{\fs55}your boy/girl dating talk at home before you come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是哦 确实需要\N{\fs55}Yeah,I probably do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你感兴趣 我可以送你一本书\N{\fs55}I'll give you a book if you're that interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,讲约会的书吗\N{\fs55}On dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,讲血液的书\N{\fs55}On blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有什么医学问题吗\N{\fs55}Another medical question perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 我觉得你是我见过最漂亮的人\N{\fs55}No. I just think you're the prettiest thing I ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为这里太黑了\N{\fs55}That's because I'm sitting in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.36,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 你就是很美\N{\fs55}No,you're just beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,闪开\N{\fs55}Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,开车看着点路啊\N{\fs55}You need to watch where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我不知道你介意\N{\fs55}I'm sorry. I didn't think you'd mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你都没说一声\N{\fs55}You didn't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我以为你会喜欢 - 那也要先说一声\N{\fs55}- I thought you might have liked it. - Well,I might have if you'd asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你不过来吗\N{\fs55}You coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么都不跟我们说一声\N{\fs55}Why didn't you say nothing to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你会试着阻止我的\N{\fs55}'Cause you would have tried and talked me out of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我知道自己没做错 - 还记得主的训诫吗\N{\fs55}- and I know what I'm doing is right. - And what about His Commandment?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是去杀人的 而是去自卫\N{\fs55}It's not killing in a war. It's protecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,教会的很多男生都去参军了\N{\fs55}Loads of boys from our church are going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是战时 国家需要男人\N{\fs55}There is a war and they need men.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在造纸厂工作 没法保家卫国\N{\fs55}And working in a paper mill ain't going to save this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的孩子像电影明星一样\N{\fs55}Looks like a movie star,our boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,军装很帅 帽子不错\N{\fs55}Nice uniform,good hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,让我想起去法国前 阿蒂·吉登斯穿军装的样子\N{\fs55}Reminds me of how Artie Giddens looked in his uniform when we went to France.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.40,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还记得他吗 Bertha - 别说了 汤姆\N{\fs55}- Remember him,Bertha? - Don't,Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs55}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想说 阿蒂穿军装潇洒极了\N{\fs55}I'm just saying how snappy Artie looked in his uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好像你们女生都这样觉得\N{\fs55}All you girls certainly seemed to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:20:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好多女生围着他 他可得瑟了\N{\fs55}He had them flocking to him. He was most proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我只希望 哈尔中枪时\N{\fs55}I just hope that when our Hal gets shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.04,0:20:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,子弹直接从夹克正面穿透\N{\fs55}it's through the front of his jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一处射入伤 不会太血腥\N{\fs55}Like a simple entry wound, not much mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,阿蒂是后背中枪的\N{\fs55}Artie got hit in the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.72,0:20:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,子弹穿膛而过 把内脏和肠子都带出来了\N{\fs55}it blew most of his guts and intestines out his front,offal everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,军装也都烂了\N{\fs55}Wrecked his uniform entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还好他死了\N{\fs55}It was lucky he was dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没有看到自己的军装被毁了\N{\fs55}so he never knew how awful his uniform looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,离我远点\N{\fs55}Get outta of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你是山羊附体吗\N{\fs55}What are you,part mountain goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底要不要帮我 戴斯蒙德·道斯\N{\fs55}Are you going to help me,Desmond Doss,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还是把我丢在下面\N{\fs55}or are you just going to leave me stranded?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以帮你 但这是有代价的\N{\fs55}I'll help you,but it's gonna cost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什么代价\N{\fs55}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.24,0:21:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,亲我一下\N{\fs55}A kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是敲诈呀 - 是的 没错\N{\fs55}- That is pure blackmail. - Well,yes,ma'am,it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但这就是我的条件\N{\fs55}But that is still my condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.44,0:22:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那就算成交了 我来拉你上去\N{\fs55}That's the deal. And I'm going to hold you to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.52,0:22:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,先等等\N{\fs55}Well,hold on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.64,0:22:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这次不会扇我了吧\N{\fs55}You ain't gonna slap me,are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为如果我掉下去 会拉着你一起的\N{\fs55}'Cause I fall off, I'm going to take you with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,亲我试试看咯\N{\fs55}Kiss me and find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.40,0:23:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs55}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我要入伍\N{\fs55}I have to enlist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能自己留下 让别人为我战斗\N{\fs55}I can't stay here while all of them go fight for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.48,0:23:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你可以留下的 - 桃乐茜 我必须参军\N{\fs55}- Yes,you can. You can stay here. - Dorothy,I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.40,0:23:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我想做军医\N{\fs55}I want to be a medic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.16,0:23:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去救人 而不是杀人\N{\fs55}I figure I'll be saving people, not killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去上班了 要迟到了\N{\fs55}I have to go to work. I'm going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.68,0:23:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,桃乐茜 宝贝\N{\fs55}Dorothy. Dorothy,darling. Dorothy. Dorothy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.76,0:23:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你到底要不要求婚呀\N{\fs55}So are you going to ask me to marry you or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 你还愿意跟我在一起吗\N{\fs55}Well,I don't know. You still going to have me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.24,0:24:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 你又没问\N{\fs55}Well,I wouldn't know, you haven't asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.48,0:24:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那我要问你 发自肺腑地问你\N{\fs55}Well,I'm asking you, with all my heart and then some.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.20,0:24:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你愿意嫁给我吗 - 是的 我愿意\N{\fs55}- Will you marry me? - Then,yes. Yes,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.00,0:24:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候\N{\fs55}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.48,0:24:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,等你第一次休假回来\N{\fs55}Soon as you get your first leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.00,0:24:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我现在还不想理你\N{\fs55}But I still don't like you at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.48,0:24:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧 - 好的\N{\fs55}- Yeah. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.36,0:24:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我爱你\N{\fs55}Okay. Well,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.08,0:24:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈让我来这找你\N{\fs55}Momma said come see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.64,0:24:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs55}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.80,0:24:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这仨人是我最铁的哥们\N{\fs55}These three were my best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.44,0:25:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从小一起长大的\N{\fs55}I grew up with 'em,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.00,0:25:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起闯祸 一起追女生\N{\fs55}I got into trouble with 'em, chased girls with 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.00,0:25:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,然后一起参军\N{\fs55}And I enlisted with 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.76,0:25:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我的朋友们都在这了\N{\fs55}Now my friends are there,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.40,0:25:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,埋在泥土之下 成为蚯蚓之食\N{\fs55}covered in dirt and grass and eaten by worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.48,0:25:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想以后来这看我的儿子\N{\fs55}I don't want to have to visit my sons here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.88,0:25:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 我已经报名了\N{\fs55}Daddy,I signed up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.44,0:25:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 我没法不去 别人都去了\N{\fs55}I couldn't do otherwise,Pop. Everybody else is doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.00,0:25:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你又不是别人\N{\fs55}You ain't everybody else!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.00,0:25:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,别人头脑一热 都没细想 就入伍了\N{\fs55}Everybody else jumps in and does things quick,without thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.00,0:25:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就像我们当年一样傻\N{\fs55}Like the damn idiot fools we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.84,0:25:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那些活下来的战士 是因为他们有能力\N{\fs55}And soldiers who live, they live because they can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.64,0:25:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你做不到的\N{\fs55}You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.76,0:25:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你总得坐下来思考 遇事要去祈祷\N{\fs55}Look,you gotta sit and think and pray about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.68,0:25:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞧瞧 你现在就在这样\N{\fs55}I mean,look at you, you're doing it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.72,0:25:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你去战场 根本活不下来的\N{\fs55}You won't be able to live with yourself if you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.88,0:25:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不去 我才没法活下去\N{\fs55}No,I won't be able to live with myself if I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.96,0:26:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我会做军医 我要这样为国效力\N{\fs55}I'm going to be a medic. That's going to be my way to serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.00,0:26:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你又来了 感觉自己都想清楚了\N{\fs55}See,there you go,thinking it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.00,0:26:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你真以为战争能容下你 能如你所想吗\N{\fs55}What,you figure this war is just going to fit in with you,your ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.44,0:26:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这肯定有难度\N{\fs55}Well,I don't doubt it's going to be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.56,0:26:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不是有难度 而是不可能\N{\fs55}It won't be hard,it'll be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.56,0:26:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你讲 不管你的脑子里有什么疯狂想法\N{\fs55}You know,whatever beliefs you have in your crazy head now,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.44,0:26:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,都不可能实现 根本不是那样的\N{\fs55}they won't ever play out. It don't work that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.68,0:26:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,即使你走运 奇迹般活下来\N{\fs55}And if by some,I don't know, miracle chance you survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.76,0:26:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不会去感谢上帝的\N{\fs55}you won't be giving no thanks to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.12,0:26:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 准备好了吗 - 好了\N{\fs55}- Ready? - Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.44,0:26:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要挤在这里\N{\fs55}Y'all need some air.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.56,0:26:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 各位 动起来 国家需要你们\N{\fs55}Come on,fellas,shake a leg. Uncle Sam's got you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.60,0:26:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,跟妈妈道别吧 快点\N{\fs55}Say goodbye to Momma. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.12,0:26:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们 不要靠近汽车了\N{\fs55}Ladies,please,step away from the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.56,0:26:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我差点忘了 给你的\N{\fs55}I almost forgot. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.08,0:26:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你带着这本圣经 这是我的\N{\fs55}I want you to have this. It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.08,0:26:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你就放在这里 把我也放这里\N{\fs55}You keep it right here,where I'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.96,0:27:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 拜拜 - 拜拜\N{\fs55}- Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.88,0:27:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fs55}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.84,0:27:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 兄弟\N{\fs55}Hey. Sorry,pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.68,0:28:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我每次回来 都得看你的畸形身材吗\N{\fs55}Do I have to gaze at your deformity every time I walk to my bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.72,0:28:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,随便看啊 随便嫉妒 老兄\N{\fs55}Gaze upon it in envy,my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.96,0:28:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗 迷路了吗 这里是空床\N{\fs55}You okay there? You look lost. Vacancy right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.64,0:28:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这边风景不错 能看到山和湖\N{\fs55}Wise choice. It's got views of the mountains down to the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.16,0:28:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫Randall Fuller\N{\fs55}Randall Fuller.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.68,0:28:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫戴斯蒙德·道斯\N{\fs55}Desmond Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.48,0:28:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他"教授" 没人懂他说的话\N{\fs55}Call him "Teach." No one understands a word he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.52,0:28:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为这里的人都不识字\N{\fs55}That's because no one else here can read.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.40,0:28:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那暴露狂管自己叫"好莱坞"\N{\fs55}The testicles there belong to a man calling himself "Hollywood."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.72,0:28:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,块头挺大 下面挺小\N{\fs55}They look like they belong to a smaller guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.24,0:28:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你还挺懂呀\N{\fs55}You know testicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.28,0:28:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 这是新鞋\N{\fs55}Oh! Hey,I just got these shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.00,0:28:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫格里瑟·诺兰 来自红钩 你是哪的人\N{\fs55}Hey,uh,Grease Nolan,outta Red Hook. Where you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.32,0:28:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 弗吉尼亚 - 乡巴佬呀\N{\fs55}- Virginia. - Ooh,hillbilly,huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.04,0:28:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你娶了你表妹吗\N{\fs55}You marry your first cousin?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.54,0:28:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我开玩笑的\N{\fs55}I'm just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.92,0:28:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那是史密提 他在教训柯辛斯基\N{\fs55}That's Smitty over there, whipping Kirzinski's ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.16,0:28:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好像你比我厉害似的 白痴\N{\fs55}Like you were doing any better,chowder head.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.64,0:28:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是想让你难看\N{\fs55}Hey,I didn't want to embarrass you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.24,0:28:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,沃尔·柯辛斯基 很高兴认识你\N{\fs55}Wal Kirzinski,nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.28,0:28:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,竹竿 你叫什么来着\N{\fs55}Hey,beanpole, what did you say your name was?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.32,0:28:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,戴斯蒙德·道斯\N{\fs55}Desmond Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.00,0:29:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那位是特克斯·刘易斯 他觉得自己是牛仔\N{\fs55}That's Tex Lewis over there, he thinks he's some kind of cowboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.00,0:29:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,维托 虽然个头不高 但是非常凶\N{\fs55}And,uh,Vito Rinnelli. He may be small,but he is a bulldog.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.80,0:29:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 - 你好啊\N{\fs55}- Hey. - How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.16,0:29:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 戴斯蒙 - 你好啊\N{\fs55}- Desmond. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.84,0:29:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这位帅哥叫乐琪·福特\N{\fs55}This handsome guy right here is Lucky Ford.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.76,0:29:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那俩自以为是赌神的 是沃克和平尼克\N{\fs55}That's Walker and Pinnick over there pretending they're card sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.76,0:29:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,消停一会 行吗 格里瑟 \N{\fs55}Pipe down,Grease,all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.24,0:29:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,别耍嘴皮子 有本事拿钱过来啊\N{\fs55}Unless you want to put your money where your mouth is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.12,0:29:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哎哟 这书不错吧\N{\fs55}Oh,hey,the old good book,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.28,0:29:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得乐琪的书也不错\N{\fs55}I think Lucky's got a good book.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.00,0:29:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是吧 乐琪 - 是一本好书\N{\fs55}- Right,Lucky? - It's a good read.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.60,0:29:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,全体集合\N{\fs55}Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.16,0:29:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,站好队 动起来\N{\fs55}Line up! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.72,0:29:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,速度点 动起来\N{\fs55}Let's go,move it. Move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.92,0:30:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你长得很奇怪啊\N{\fs55}You are a very strange-looking individual
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.96,0:30:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,别介意我这样说 列兵\N{\fs55}if you don't mind me saying so,Private.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.84,0:30:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你叫什么 - 安迪·沃克\N{\fs55}- Name? - Andy Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.12,0:30:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经死多久了 小子\N{\fs55}How long have you been dead,son?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.20,0:30:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 长官 - 我不是"长官"\N{\fs55}- Sir? - I am not "Sir"!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.36,0:30:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我豪威尔中士 没用的人才叫长官\N{\fs55}I am Sergeant Howell or Sarge. "Sir" you save for useless people.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.16,0:30:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你说自己叫"食尸鬼"吗 - 我叫沃克 中士\N{\fs55}- The name is "Ghoul," you say? - Walker,Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.48,0:30:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就叫食尸鬼了 - 好的 中士\N{\fs55}- Ghoul it is. - Yes,Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.28,0:30:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来有点不对劲 列兵\N{\fs55}There's something off in your presentation,Private.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.16,0:30:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,说不出来哪有问题\N{\fs55}Can't place it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.80,0:30:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的头发吗\N{\fs55}Is it your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.40,0:30:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,还是裤子有褶了\N{\fs55}Is it the wrinkle in your trousers?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.92,0:31:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我脚上有一把刀 中士\N{\fs55}I have a knife in my foot,Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.40,0:31:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是哦 就是这里了 有一把刀\N{\fs55}Oh,yes,of course,that's it. The knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.12,0:31:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你叫什么名字 - 史密提·莱克(\N{\fs55}- What is your name,soldier? - Smitty Ryker.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.04,0:31:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你叫蠢货列兵 知道为什么吗\N{\fs55}No,your name is Private Idiot. Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.84,0:31:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- 因为我脚上有一把刀 - 谁插上去的 列兵\N{\fs55}- Because I have a knife in my foot. - Who placed the knife there,Private?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.80,0:31:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,中士 这是意外 我们在切磋的\N{\fs55}It was an accident,Sarge. We was playing Stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.56,0:31:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我很欣慰 竟然不是你自己插上去的\N{\fs55}I am heartened by the knowledge you did not place it there with intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.84,0:31:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁扔的刀\N{\fs55}Who threw the knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.76,0:31:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 中士 列兵柯辛斯基\N{\fs55}I did,Sergeant. Private Kirzinski.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.08,0:31:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你有印第安血统吧 是哪个部落的 小子\N{\fs55}You look part Indian. To what tribe do you belong,son?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.88,0:31:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我是波兰人\N{\fs55}No,I'm Polish.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.28,0:31:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 你准有彻罗基族或萧尼族血统\N{\fs55}Wrong. I believe you must have Cherokee or Shawnee blood in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.56,0:31:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有 中士 - 你在跟我顶嘴吗\N{\fs55}- No,Sergeant. - Are you contradicting me,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.36,0:31:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你这傻逼混帐东西 - 不是 中士\N{\fs55}- you wagon-burning son of a bitch? - No,Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.12,0:31:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,让我听听印第安人的战阵呐喊 小子\N{\fs55}Let me see your Indian war cry,son.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.12,0:31:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会...\N{\fs55}I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.92,0:31:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大声点 让我听听\N{\fs55}Louder! Let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.08,0:31:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你的野兽精神呢 你是花纹蛇吗\N{\fs55}What is your animal spirit? Are you a garter snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.00,0:31:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 中士 - 你是花栗鼠吗\N{\fs55}- No,Sergeant! - Are you a chipmunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.52,0:31:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 中士 - 你是跳舞的麋鹿吗\N{\fs55}- No,Sergeant! - Are you a dancing reindeer?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.08,0:31:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 中士 - 你是在顶嘴吗 列兵\N{\fs55}- No,Sergeant! - Are you contradicting me,Private?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.40,0:31:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是 中士 - 很好\N{\fs55}- No,Sergeant! - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.12,0:32:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那从此以后 我就叫你"酋长"了\N{\fs55}Then I shall henceforth call you "Chief"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.36,0:32:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,以示对你们部族的尊重\N{\fs55}as a sign of great respect to your people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.96,0:32:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 中士\N{\fs55}Thank you,Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.12,0:32:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,小子 你在笑我吗 还是你本来就很爱笑\N{\fs55}Are you grinning at me,boy, or is that your natural state?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.44,0:32:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不 中士\N{\fs55}No,Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.52,0:32:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你叫什么 - 戴斯蒙德·道斯\N{\fs55}- Name,Private? - Desmond Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.80,0:32:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我见过比你更壮的玉米秆\N{\fs55}I have seen stalks of corn with better physiques.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.48,0:32:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,搞得我想把你的耳朵拧掉 列兵\N{\fs55}Makes me want to pull an ear off,Private.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.96,0:32:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你能背动你这样重的人吗 - 是的 中士\N{\fs55}- Can you carry your weight? - Yes,Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.08,0:32:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么瘦 当然简单\N{\fs55}Should be easy for you,then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.32,0:32:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 下士 - 中士\N{\fs55}- Corporal. - Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.60,0:32:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,记得别让这小子被大风刮跑了\N{\fs55}Make sure you keep this man away from strong winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.92,0:32:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 中士\N{\fs55}Yes,Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.48,0:32:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 蠢货列兵 - 是的 中士\N{\fs55}- Private Idiot. - Yes,Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.32,0:32:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,抬起脚来 抬高一点\N{\fs55}Raise your foot. Higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.04,0:32:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都出去 赶紧的 动起来\N{\fs55}Everyone outside. Now! Move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.08,0:32:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我说赶紧动起来\N{\fs55}I said move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.28,0:32:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我先穿上军装 中士\N{\fs55}All right. Just getting in my uniform,Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.80,0:32:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我让他穿了吗 下士 - 好像没有 中士\N{\fs55}- Did I ask him to,Corporal? - No memory of it,Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.48,0:32:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信喜欢在屋里光着屁股的人\N{\fs55}I believe any man who takes such pride in his natural naked state
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.00,0:32:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定也喜欢到外面吹吹风\N{\fs55}will surely enjoy the brisk of the outdoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.40,0:32:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,光着老二出去吧 二等兵\N{\fs55}Now move your privates,Private Parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.52,0:33:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,快一点 暴露狂\N{\fs55}Move it! You son of an exhibitionist!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.48,0:33:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,下面要教你们 如何系单套结\N{\fs55}I am going to teach you how to tie a bowline knot,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.96,0:33:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些废物就能从高地下来了\N{\fs55}so you can get your sorry asses down from a height,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.16,0:33:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我就能继续教训你们了\N{\fs55}so I may then kick them!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.36,0:33:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,绕一个圈 这是兔子洞\N{\fs55}Create a loop. This is the rabbit hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.52,0:33:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,兔子逃出洞 绕树跑一圈\N{\fs55}The rabbit comes out of his hole, runs around the tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.24,0:33:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,又回到洞里 开始吧\N{\fs55}goes back into the hole. All right,let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.04,0:33:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,做得不错 特克斯\N{\fs55}Very good,Tex.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.04,0:33:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,加把劲 教授\N{\fs55}Keep struggling,Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.56,0:33:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你套过山羊吗 好莱坞\N{\fs55}Have you ever roped a goat,Hollywood?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.96,0:33:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 中士\N{\fs55}No,Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.89,0:33:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你凝视过山羊的眼睛吗\N{\fs55}Have you ever looked into a goat's eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.52,0:33:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有 中士 - 很好 否则就太变态了\N{\fs55}- No,Sarge. - Good,that would be unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.04,0:33:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道如果继续憋气 你会死掉吧\N{\fs55}You know if you don't breathe, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.76,0:33:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不错 蠢货列兵\N{\fs55}Good,Private Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.36,0:33:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,祝贺你 小胖墩 你刚从50英尺的地方摔断了脖子\N{\fs55}Congratulations, Greaseball,you just fell 50 feet and broke your neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.64,0:33:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮 列兵维托\N{\fs55}Brilliant,Private Vito Rinnelli.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.24,0:33:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚把自己勒死了 白痴\N{\fs55}You strangled yourself,numb nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.92,0:33:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是墨索里尼的粉丝吗 - 不是 中士\N{\fs55}- Are you a fan of Benito? - No,Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.76,0:34:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那就长高点 美国人都要更魁梧\N{\fs55}A bit taller. If you were American,you'd be taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.28,0:34:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,道斯 这是什么玩意 一边奶子一个吗\N{\fs55}What've we got here,Doss, one for each titty?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.44,0:34:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在打绳结 不是编胸罩\N{\fs55}You were tying a bowline,boy, not building a bra!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.40,0:34:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很好笑吗 下士 - 我不知道 中士\N{\fs55}- What is so funny,Corporal? - Couldn't tell you,Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.60,0:34:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 小姑娘似的 跑起来 快跟上\N{\fs55}Come on! Come on,ladies, pick it up! Move it! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.88,0:34:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我要看到你们的热情 快加把劲\N{\fs55}I want to see some fire here. A little hustle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.60,0:34:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,拿出点本事来\N{\fs55}Show me something!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.08,0:34:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,跑起来\N{\fs55}Run like you mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.36,0:34:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 下去 快点 - 快点 跑起来\N{\fs55}- Down,down,down! Faster,faster! - Come on. Move it! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.20,0:34:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 小伙子们 洗澡时间\N{\fs55}Let's go,it's bath time,boys! It's bath time!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.08,0:34:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快爬 快爬\N{\fs55}Move! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.00,0:34:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看你们的本事 快点\N{\fs55}I want to see you work. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.16,0:34:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 快点\N{\fs55}Dig,dig,dig!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.88,0:34:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别让后面追上了 跑起来\N{\fs55}Don't forget behind your ears. Let's go. Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.44,0:34:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像挺享受的 裸体原始人\N{\fs55}I bet you're enjoying this, you naked degenerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.20,0:34:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 动起来\N{\fs55}Let's go! Hustle. Hustle. Hustle. Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.96,0:34:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,跑起来 你在等什么 跑起来\N{\fs55}Let's go! What are we waiting on? Let's go! Move your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.68,0:35:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,蹬住木头 翻墙过去 别被扎到了\N{\fs55}Get the wood! Get the wall! Don't get splinters!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.72,0:35:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,冲啊\N{\fs55}Drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.20,0:35:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,冲啊\N{\fs55}Drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.64,0:35:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 你还好吗\N{\fs55}Jeez,are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.04,0:35:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\fs55}Yeah,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.04,0:35:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 提起精神来 - 跑起来 快点\N{\fs55}- Some spirit here,boys. Move! - Come on,move!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.72,0:35:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你脑子有病吗 让你休息了吗\N{\fs55}What the hell is wrong with you? No one said take a rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.72,0:35:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑到终点线去 快点\N{\fs55}Move your asses to the finish line! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.04,0:35:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,冲刺 冲刺\N{\fs55}Hustle! Hustle!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.00,0:35:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,跑到终点去\N{\fs55}Get your asses across that line!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.40,0:35:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,时间到 干得不错 道斯\N{\fs55}Time! Nice work,Doss!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.40,0:35:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是美国政府给你们的礼物\N{\fs55}This is a personal gift from the United States government
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.76,0:35:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,每人一把\N{\fs55}to each and every one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.52,0:35:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,标准的美国步枪 7.62毫米口径 M1型\N{\fs55}A standard issue U.S. rifle, caliber .30,M1,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.20,0:35:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,自动上膛的半自动肩扛式武器\N{\fs55}a clip-fed,shoulder-fired, semi-automatic weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.48,0:35:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,专门设计用来杀敌的\N{\fs55}designed to bring death and destruction to the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.28,0:35:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这将会成为你们的爱人 情人 情妇\N{\fs55}This is to be your lover, your mistress,your concubine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.16,0:35:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,也许会成为你们此生的真爱\N{\fs55}Perhaps the only thing in life you will ever truly love.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.20,0:36:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟们 舞会开始 来挑女伴吧\N{\fs55}Fellas,let's dance. Grab a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.52,0:36:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,枪口别朝前\N{\fs55}Don't point your gun forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.64,0:36:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天可不想中枪\N{\fs55}I do not want to be shot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.80,0:36:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,即使你们想给我一枪\N{\fs55}No matter how much you are tempted.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.16,0:36:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,把枪立在身体侧面\N{\fs55}Place the weapon by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.20,0:36:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,都注意\N{\fs55}Pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.24,0:36:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗 玉米杆\N{\fs55}Problem,Private Corn Stalk?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.84,0:36:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,大小不合适 还是颜色不喜欢\N{\fs55}Is there not one in your size, or is it the color that is the issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.76,0:36:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不 中士\N{\fs55}No,Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.72,0:36:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们跟我说 不是必须扛枪\N{\fs55}I was... I was told I don't have to carry a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.32,0:36:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,再说一遍 你走近点 我肯定是听错了\N{\fs55}Come again? Step forward,Private. I can't be hearing this right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.12,0:36:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉 中士\N{\fs55}Well,I'm sorry,Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.52,0:36:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能碰枪\N{\fs55}I can't touch a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.24,0:36:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是什么问题\N{\fs55}What exactly is the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.76,0:36:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没有问题 只是搞错了\N{\fs55}No problem,just a mistake,sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.96,0:36:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我参军时 已经说明过了\N{\fs55}I told the Army when I joined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.08,0:36:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那不可能\N{\fs55}That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.76,0:37:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道为什么不可能吗 列兵\N{\fs55}Do you know why it's not possible,Private?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.04,0:37:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道 长官\N{\fs55}No,sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.52,0:37:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,因为美国军队是不会犯错的\N{\fs55}Because the United States Army does not make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.24,0:37:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果出了问题 那就是你的问题\N{\fs55}So if there's a problem, you must be that problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.52,0:37:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不应该被编入步枪连队\N{\fs55}I was just never supposed to be sent to a rifle company.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.68,0:37:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他因信仰拒服兵役 长官\N{\fs55}He's a C.O.,sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.32,0:37:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你因为信仰拒服兵役 却跑来参军\N{\fs55}You're a conscientious objector, and you joined the Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.24,0:37:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 长官 我是尽职的合作者\N{\fs55}Well,no,sir, I'm a conscientious cooperator.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.64,0:37:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在逗我吗 道斯 - 不是 长官 我是自愿参军的\N{\fs55}- Are you screwing with me,Doss? - No. No,sir. I volunteered.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.60,0:37:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意穿军装\N{\fs55}I ain't got no problem with wearing my uniform,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.48,0:37:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,致敬国旗 尽职尽责 这些都没问题\N{\fs55}or saluting the flag and doing my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.60,0:37:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是做不到开枪杀人\N{\fs55}It's just carrying a gun and the taking of human life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.80,0:37:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你只是不杀人吗 - 是的 长官\N{\fs55}- You don't kill? That's all. - Yes,sir,that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.60,0:37:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道战争会死伤众多吧\N{\fs55}You know quite a bit of killing does occur in a war?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.32,0:37:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 长官\N{\fs55}Yes,sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.44,0:37:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,杀戮是战争的本质\N{\fs55}I mean, that is the essential nature of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.48,0:37:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 长官 - 好吧\N{\fs55}- Yes,sir. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.80,0:38:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你对美国军队还有什么要求吗\N{\fs55}Do you have any other requirements of the United States Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.20,0:38:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还能做些什么\N{\fs55}Is there anything else that we can do to ensure
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.04,0:38:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,才能让你舒服地留下来\N{\fs55}that you have a comfortable stay here with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.76,0:38:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他想周六休息 长官\N{\fs55}He doesn't want to work on Saturdays,sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.72,0:38:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我是基督复临安息日会的\N{\fs55}Well,Saturdays... I'm a Seventh-day Adventist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.04,0:38:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,周六是我的安息日 所以我不能干活\N{\fs55}So,Saturday is my Sabbath, so I'm not allowed to work then.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.12,0:38:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这不是问题 你说呢 中士\N{\fs55}I don't think that poses a problem, do you,Sergeant?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.64,0:38:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,干脆告诉敌人 安息日不要进攻\N{\fs55}We shall simply ask the enemy not to invade on the Sabbath,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.36,0:38:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,因为列兵道斯要祈祷\N{\fs55}'cause Private Doss here is at prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.32,0:38:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们都搞清楚了\N{\fs55}All right. Now we got that clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.36,0:38:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我来说说我的要求\N{\fs55}Now let me tell you my requirements.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.36,0:38:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,其实很简单 不像你的那么复杂\N{\fs55}They're not as complicated as yours. They're very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.64,0:38:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你还在我们连队里 在我的手下当兵\N{\fs55}As long as you're in this company, under my command,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.68,0:38:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就必须服从我的命令 就这样\N{\fs55}you will obey my orders. Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.76,0:38:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你在这做不到 在战场上也没法指望你\N{\fs55}If you can't do it here, I can't trust you to do it in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.08,0:38:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我将按照第八条例 以精神问题开除你\N{\fs55}I'm putting you in for a Section 8,psychiatric discharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.84,0:38:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,解散\N{\fs55}Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.88,0:38:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们\N{\fs55}Gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.88,0:39:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,大家来看看列兵戴斯蒙德·道斯\N{\fs55}I want you to meet Private Desmond Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.72,0:39:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,很显然 列兵道斯并不崇尚武力\N{\fs55}Apparently, Private Doss does not believe in violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.96,0:39:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他也不会使用武力\N{\fs55}He does not practice violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.92,0:39:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至不愿意屈尊碰枪\N{\fs55}He will not even deign to touch a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.24,0:39:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵道斯因为信仰拒服兵役\N{\fs55}You see, Private Doss is a conscientious objector.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.88,0:39:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,所以告诫各位 别指望他在战场上救你们\N{\fs55}So I plead with you, do not look to him to save you on the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.92,0:39:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他肯定会忙着跟良心作斗争\N{\fs55}because he will undoubtedly be too busy wrestling with his conscience to assist.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.40,0:39:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 中士 不是那样的 - 不许插嘴\N{\fs55}- Sarge, that's not true. - Private, as you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.92,0:39:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们会有人对此有意见\N{\fs55}Now, I realize some of you might have strong feelings about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.60,0:39:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们正是因此而战\N{\fs55}It is what we men fight for.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.92,0:39:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,去维护我们的权利 保护女人和孩子\N{\fs55}To defend our rights, and to protect our women and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.88,0:39:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,即使列兵道斯的信仰 会夺走女人和孩子的生命\N{\fs55}Even if Private Doss' beliefs might cause women and children to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.96,0:39:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我希望连里的每一个人\N{\fs55}So I will expect everyone in this company
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.56,0:39:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,都能给列兵道斯足够的尊重\N{\fs55}to give Private Doss the full measure of respect he is due
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.92,0:40:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,反正他很快就要走了\N{\fs55}for the short time he will be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.00,0:40:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我说清楚了吗\N{\fs55}Am I clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.60,0:40:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 中士\N{\fs55}Yes, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.44,0:40:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿的什么 Dessie\N{\fs55}What'cha got there, Dessie?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.80,0:40:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那是什么\N{\fs55}You know what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.08,0:40:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这本有点小呢\N{\fs55}It just seems kind of small.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.28,0:40:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,小本圣经 给小男人看\N{\fs55}It's half the Bible for half the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.00,0:40:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,史密提 看在上帝份上 把圣经还给他吧\N{\fs55}For Pete's sake, Smitty, give him back his Bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.68,0:40:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我又没跟你说话\N{\fs55}I don't remember speaking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.48,0:40:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你不打架 觉得比我们高尚吗\N{\fs55}So, how come you don't fight? You think you're better than us?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.56,0:40:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs55}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.60,0:40:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有人打你呢\N{\fs55}What if you was attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.80,0:40:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这样\N{\fs55}Say, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.20,0:40:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,圣经让你把另一边脸也转过来吗\N{\fs55}The Bible says to turn the other cheek, don't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.60,0:40:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我觉得这不是信仰问题\N{\fs55}See, I don't think this is a question of religion, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.80,0:40:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你就是懦夫 就这么简单\N{\fs55}I think this is cowardice, plain and simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.68,0:41:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,道斯 对吗 你是胆小鬼吧\N{\fs55}Is that right, Doss? Are you chickenshit, that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.80,0:41:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊 打我\N{\fs55}Go on, take a poke.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.40,0:41:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吧 我让你两只手\N{\fs55}Tell you what, I'm going to give you a free shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.84,0:41:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样\N{\fs55}Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.44,0:41:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,打我啊 来打我 道斯\N{\fs55}Hit me, Doss. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.20,0:41:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 快去打他 - 快上啊\N{\fs55}- Let him have it. - Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.64,0:41:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不来吗\N{\fs55}No?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.64,0:41:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,胆小鬼\N{\fs55}Chickenshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.28,0:41:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是啥啊\N{\fs55}Hold on here. What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.92,0:41:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还给我\N{\fs55}Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.32,0:41:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 妹子长得不错呀 - 可以啊\N{\fs55}- This is a fine-looking broad. - Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.24,0:41:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,传来给我们看看\N{\fs55}Hey, pass it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.88,0:41:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的美妞 就该配一个真正的男人\N{\fs55}Now, this would be the kind of broad that deserves a real man.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.28,0:41:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,快还给我\N{\fs55}Give me that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.56,0:41:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,求我\N{\fs55}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.40,0:41:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了\N{\fs55}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.24,0:41:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"求你还给我 史密提"\N{\fs55}"Please give it back, Smitty."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.72,0:41:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,求你还给我 史密提\N{\fs55}Please give it back, Smitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.32,0:42:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你有幻听吗 戴斯蒙\N{\fs55}Do you hear voices, Desmond?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.40,0:42:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 长官\N{\fs55}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.20,0:42:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,根据我的理解 上帝会跟你说话 是吗\N{\fs55}But I understand that God talks to you. Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.92,0:42:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,长官 我不是疯子\N{\fs55}Sir, I'm not a crazy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.72,0:42:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是觉得 所有人都把你当成疯子\N{\fs55}Is that how you feel most people regard you, a crazy person?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.52,0:42:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道自己有点不同 但是...\N{\fs55}I'm different. I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.24,0:42:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会装出另一副模样\N{\fs55}I'm not going to pretend to be something I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.52,0:42:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我就是我 - 听起来挺孤独的\N{\fs55}- I am what I am. - Sounds lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.32,0:42:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你孤独吗\N{\fs55}You lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.32,0:42:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 所以你没有幻听 - 没有 长官\N{\fs55}- So, you don't hear voices. - No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.20,0:42:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我向上帝祈祷 希望他能听见 但那不是对话\N{\fs55}I pray to God and I like to think He hears me, but it ain't a conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.52,0:42:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不像我们现在假装在做的\N{\fs55}like the one we're pretending to have right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.44,0:42:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 假装吗 - 是的 长官\N{\fs55}- Pretending, Private? - Well, yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.36,0:42:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你是想按第八条例 把我从部队开除\N{\fs55}I know all you really want to do is give me a Section 8,drum me out of the Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.60,0:42:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的脑子没问题 只是在坚持信仰\N{\fs55}but I'm not off up above. I just simply believe what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.16,0:43:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在试着理解你 好吗\N{\fs55}Well, I'm trying to understand, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.20,0:43:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是上帝告诉你 不要碰枪的吗\N{\fs55}Was it God who told you not to pick up a rifle?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.24,0:43:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝说 不要杀戮\N{\fs55}God says not to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.48,0:43:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那是最重要的诫命之一\N{\fs55}That's one of His most important Commandments.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.32,0:43:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,大部分人会理解成 不能谋杀\N{\fs55}Most people take that to mean, "Don't commit murder."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.96,0:43:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而战争完全是另一码事\N{\fs55}War is a completely different set of circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.40,0:43:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,耶稣说过 我给你们一条新诫命\N{\fs55}Jesus said, "A new Commandment I give unto you,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.96,0:43:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是让你们彼此相爱 如同我爱你们\N{\fs55}that you love one another, just as I have loved you."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.08,0:43:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要对抗的 那可是撒旦\N{\fs55}This is Satan himself we're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.28,0:43:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,作为基督徒 你应该明白的\N{\fs55}Surely, as a good Christian, you can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.64,0:43:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道的 所以我才来参军\N{\fs55}I can see that, sir, and that is why I joined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.48,0:43:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但很抱歉 我不会碰武器的\N{\fs55}But I'm sorry, I will not bear arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.32,0:43:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他的宗教观很独特\N{\fs55}His religious views are certainly unique,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.08,0:43:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但还不满足第八条例的驱逐条件\N{\fs55}but they do not constitute grounds for a Section 8 discharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.68,0:43:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有这样的人在 我怎么维持纪律\N{\fs55}How am I supposed to maintain discipline with a man like that in my unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.80,0:43:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs55}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.36,0:43:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但他是出于信仰拒服兵役\N{\fs55}But he is a legitimate conscientious objector,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.72,0:43:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,必须允许他做医务兵\N{\fs55}and he must be allowed to work as a combat medic,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.16,0:43:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,只要他能通过其他所有科目的训练\N{\fs55}provided he qualifies in all other areas of his training.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.80,0:44:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们可以权当认同他的想法\N{\fs55}Perhaps we could help make believe in his idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.56,0:44:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 把他扔到营房和炊事班吧\N{\fs55}Yeah, you restrict him to barracks and KP.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.32,0:44:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,再跟你扯上帝 就让他尝尝地狱的滋味\N{\fs55}If he throws God at you, you throw hell right at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.76,0:44:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我要让他滚\N{\fs55}I want him gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.12,0:44:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,道斯 你这里太乱了 简直是猪圈\N{\fs55}Doss, your area is a disgrace. It's a pig sty!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.84,0:44:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好笑吗 莱克 - 不 中士\N{\fs55}- Something funny, Ryker? - No, Sarge!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.60,0:44:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的脑子里有屎吗 - 不 中士\N{\fs55}- You got some shit on your mind? - No, Sarge!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.72,0:44:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都没有认识到\N{\fs55}What you men fail to recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.88,0:44:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,连队的水平是由最弱的人决定的\N{\fs55}is a unit is no better than its weakest member!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.72,0:44:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,得让你们长点脑子 这周末都不准请假\N{\fs55}Now, to help you learn that lesson, there will be no passes this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.12,0:44:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,都去炊事班帮厨\N{\fs55}You will all be on KP!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.64,0:44:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在所有人都去20英里全装越野\N{\fs55}Right now, everybody in full gear for a 20-mile hike.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.12,0:44:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,出发\N{\fs55}Let's go! Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.68,0:45:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把头抬起来\N{\fs55}Get your heads right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.76,0:45:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不要一副可怜相\N{\fs55}Don't start feeling sorry for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.04,0:45:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜兮兮的样子 让我看着恶心\N{\fs55}Makes me sick see you feel sorry for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.20,0:45:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们根本不知道什么叫累\N{\fs55}You dogs don't know what tired is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.60,0:45:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不倒下 谁也不准停\N{\fs55}We're going to keep going till I drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.52,0:45:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别打了 我还要睡觉呢\N{\fs55}Hey, knock it off. Trying to sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.76,0:45:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别碰我 - 好吧\N{\fs55}- Get off me. Get off me. - Okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.08,0:45:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么还在这\N{\fs55}Why the hell are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.16,0:45:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,原地不用动\N{\fs55}As you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.00,0:46:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,道斯去哪了\N{\fs55}Where's Doss?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.64,0:46:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这样对谁都没好处\N{\fs55}This isn't good for anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.28,0:46:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这也不是我参军的目的\N{\fs55}Sure ain't what I joined up for.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.00,0:46:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这跟你为什么参军没关系\N{\fs55}It's not about what you joined up for.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.84,0:46:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这关乎这里所有人的性命\N{\fs55}It's about the lives of every man in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.84,0:46:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也包括你的性命 你该退出了\N{\fs55}And yours, son. It's time to quit this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.08,0:46:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,穿好衣服 我送你出去\N{\fs55}Finish getting dressed and I'll walk you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.32,0:46:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的 道斯\N{\fs55}It's okay, Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.64,0:46:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这一点也不丢人\N{\fs55}There's no shame in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.76,0:47:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fs55}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.08,0:47:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天要站岗 早晨还要去帮厨 所以...\N{\fs55}I got extra guard duty today, and I'm on KP this morning, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.88,0:47:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能走\N{\fs55}Can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.32,0:47:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 道斯\N{\fs55}All right, Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.92,0:47:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵道斯 你能认出打你的人吗\N{\fs55}Private Doss, can you identify the men that beat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.04,0:47:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不能 中士\N{\fs55}No, Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.96,0:47:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你不知道谁揍了你吗\N{\fs55}Are you saying that you don't know who attacked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.20,0:47:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没说过 我被人揍过 中士\N{\fs55}I never said I was attacked, Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.72,0:47:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在说什么 道斯\N{\fs55}Well, what the hell are you saying, Doss?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.80,0:47:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你睡觉搞出半身淤青吗\N{\fs55}You bruised half your body sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.96,0:48:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我睡觉不老实\N{\fs55}I... I sleep pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.60,0:48:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs55}Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.84,0:48:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,周末要湿身的人 记得带安全套\N{\fs55}If you plan on getting wet this weekend, make sure you put on a hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.24,0:48:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个\N{\fs55}Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.72,0:48:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要带着一身奶味回来\N{\fs55}Don't want anyone coming back pissing cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.92,0:48:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你的咖啡里不加点奶吗 中士\N{\fs55}What, you don't want none for your coffee, Sarge?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.28,0:48:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要不现在来一发 史密提\N{\fs55}How about a shot right now, Smitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.96,0:48:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的经验之谈吗 中士\N{\fs55}You speaking from experience, Sarge?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.96,0:48:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那你得回去问问你妈了 小胖墩\N{\fs55}You'd have to ask your mom about that, Greaseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.84,0:48:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,稍息\N{\fs55}At ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.68,0:48:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵道斯 很抱歉 我不能准你的假\N{\fs55}Private Doss, I'm afraid I can't authorize your pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.56,0:48:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,通过基础训练的人 才可以享受休假\N{\fs55}This is a furlough for men who have passed the basic training.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.00,0:48:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,长官 无意冒犯 我都通过了\N{\fs55}Well, sir, respectfully, sir, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.88,0:48:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,三周之前 我就申请休假了\N{\fs55}I put in for this furlough three weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.28,0:48:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天下午要结婚\N{\fs55}I'm getting married this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.56,0:48:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这里写着 你没通过步枪考核\N{\fs55}It says you're not rifle qualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.72,0:49:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,长官 我可以不持枪的 施特尔策上校说...\N{\fs55}Well, I'm not required to carry a rifle, sir. Colonel Stelzer, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.52,0:49:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,施特尔策上校说的是...\N{\fs55}Colonel Stelzer's determination was...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.88,0:49:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,必须允许道斯做医务兵\N{\fs55}"Doss must be allowed to work as a combat medic,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.84,0:49:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,只要他能通过其他所有科目的训练\N{\fs55}provided he qualifies in all other areas of his training."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.20,0:49:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但你还没通过步枪考核\N{\fs55}And you have not qualified on the rifle range, Private.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.00,0:49:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,显而易见\N{\fs55}Pretty clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.20,0:49:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看 你知道如何持枪 我就准你的假\N{\fs55}Show me you know how to handle a rifle and I'll sign your furlough.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.32,0:49:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 坎农下士 - 到\N{\fs55}- Corporal Cannon. - Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.36,0:49:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的步枪给列兵道斯\N{\fs55}Hand Private Doss your firearm.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.92,0:49:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不会碰枪的 长官 - 我不是在跟你商量呢\N{\fs55}- I won't touch a rifle, sir. - I'm not asking you, Private!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.20,0:49:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这是连队指挥官的命令\N{\fs55}That is a direct order from a company commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.96,0:49:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,道斯 别胡闹了 你退出吧\N{\fs55}For God's sake, Doss, you stop this nonsense and quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.28,0:49:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,拒绝的话 我只能把你送上军事法庭了\N{\fs55}Refuse, and I will have no recourse but to court-martial you,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.32,0:50:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,战争期间 你只能在军事监狱里蹲着了\N{\fs55}and you will spend the duration of the war in a military prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.00,0:50:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,长官 我做不到\N{\fs55}I can't, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.20,0:50:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你还想等多长时间 桃乐茜\N{\fs55}How much longer would you like to wait, Dorothy?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.40,0:50:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我想已经足够久了\N{\fs55}I think it's been long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.00,0:50:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs55}I'm so very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.00,0:50:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候 男人就是会退缩的\N{\fs55}Sometimes men just get cold feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.44,0:50:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有些男人会 但我的戴斯蒙不会\N{\fs55}Some men might. Not my Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.28,0:51:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能会觉得 我是大混蛋\N{\fs55}You probably think I'm a real son of a bitch
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.24,0:51:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只在乎规章 不关心下属\N{\fs55}who cares only about regulations and not his men.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.12,0:51:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,能让我看看吗\N{\fs55}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.24,0:51:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也相信这本书 像其他人一样\N{\fs55}I believe in this book as much as any man.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.16,0:51:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,像其他人一样 我的良心也会纠结\N{\fs55}And just like any man, I wrestle with my conscience,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.96,0:51:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但当你珍视的一切遭受摧残时 你怎么办\N{\fs55}but what do you do when everything you value in this world is under attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.96,0:51:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 长官\N{\fs55}I don't know, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.96,0:51:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如此深刻的问题 我没法回答\N{\fs55}I ain't got answers to questions that big,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.24,0:51:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但我感觉 我的价值观也在遭受摧残\N{\fs55}but I also feel like my values are under attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.04,0:51:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道为什么\N{\fs55}and I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.64,0:51:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管你有什么原则 因为日本人不会在乎\N{\fs55}I don't give a rat's ass about your principles because the Japs don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.72,0:51:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果日本人攻击你和受伤的战友\N{\fs55}If one of them attacks you and some wounded soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.04,0:51:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你会怎么办\N{\fs55}what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.04,0:52:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的圣经去打他吗\N{\fs55}Hit him with your Bible?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.16,0:52:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备好为战友们牺牲了\N{\fs55}I'm prepared to give my life for my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.48,0:52:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,光靠牺牲 是没法打赢战争的\N{\fs55}You don't win wars by giving up your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.12,0:52:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我来这里 只因为我不想看你烂在监狱里\N{\fs55}Look, I'm only here because I don't want to see you rotting in a prison cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.04,0:52:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,认罪吧 请求法庭宽恕\N{\fs55}Plead guilty, throw yourself at the mercy of the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.68,0:52:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他们能让你回家祈祷\N{\fs55}Maybe they'll let you go home and pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.40,0:52:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,让那些勇士去赢得这场战争吧\N{\fs55}Let the brave men out there go and win this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.00,0:52:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我没法说服你 也许她可以\N{\fs55}If I can't convince you, maybe she can.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.60,0:52:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不让我给你打电话\N{\fs55}They wouldn't let me call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.40,0:52:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道 这不是你的错\N{\fs55}I knew it wasn't your making.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.68,0:52:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们对你做了什么\N{\fs55}What have they done to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.04,0:52:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 我没事的\N{\fs55}It's okay, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.68,0:52:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只是对墙打了几拳 但拳头没墙硬\N{\fs55}I just went a couple of rounds with the wall and lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.00,0:52:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说 你可能会进监狱的 Desmond\N{\fs55}They're saying you could go to prison, Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.28,0:52:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,去军事监狱\N{\fs55}Leavenworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.40,0:53:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定还有其他办法的\N{\fs55}There must be some other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.40,0:53:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道还有什么办法\N{\fs55}I don't know what that could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.32,0:53:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要求的 我都做到了 除了那件事\N{\fs55}I've done everything they asked me, except this one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.52,0:53:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不想杀人 就被当成罪犯了\N{\fs55}and I'm being treated like a criminal just 'cause I won't kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.20,0:53:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你努力过了 没人能反驳这一点\N{\fs55}You tried. Nobody can say you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.60,0:53:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但在监狱里 你能救谁呢\N{\fs55}But who are you going to save in prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.64,0:53:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,也许谁都救不了\N{\fs55}Probably nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.88,0:53:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么不能拿起破枪 装装样子呢\N{\fs55}Then why can't you just pick up the stupid gun and wave it around?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.72,0:53:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用开枪 这样也算折中了\N{\fs55}You don't have to use it, just meet them halfway.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.40,0:53:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我做不到 - 你可以的 只是面子问题\N{\fs55}- I can't do that. - Yes, you can. It's just pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.80,0:53:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不要骄傲固执 不要误解上帝的意愿\N{\fs55}Pride and stubbornness. Don't confuse your will with the Lord's.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.08,0:53:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我骄傲吗\N{\fs55}Have I been prideful?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.60,0:53:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,或许是吧\N{\fs55}Maybe I am prideful.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.60,0:53:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但这样的话 我无法继续活下去\N{\fs55}But I don't know how I'm going to live with myself
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.44,0:53:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须忠于我的信仰\N{\fs55}if I don't stay true to what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.16,0:54:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,更不用说 如何与你共度余生\N{\fs55}Much less how you could live with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.40,0:54:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你眼中的我 将达不到我的自我预期\N{\fs55}I'd never be the man that I want to be in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.44,0:54:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我会爱上你 是因为你与众不同\N{\fs55}I fell in love with you because you weren't like anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.80,0:54:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不会随波逐流\N{\fs55}and you didn't try to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.16,0:54:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不要认为 你会让我失望\N{\fs55}Do not think for one moment that you will disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.44,0:54:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何 我都会爱你\N{\fs55}I will love you no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.60,0:54:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道他要怎么办 他肯定赢不了\N{\fs55}I don't know what he's gonna do. He loses no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.52,0:54:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想让他认罪\N{\fs55}They want him to plead guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.84,0:54:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来 他会被开除军籍\N{\fs55}but then he'll get a dishonorable discharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.08,0:54:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果反抗 他肯定会被判刑\N{\fs55}Otherwise he fights them, and he for sure goes to prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.76,0:55:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样 他都会被看作懦夫\N{\fs55}Either way,they'll call him a coward
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.76,0:55:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定没法忍受这些\N{\fs55}and I don't see how he can live with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.72,0:55:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,桃乐茜 谢谢\N{\fs55}Well,thank you,Dorothy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.92,0:55:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你有机会跟他说话\N{\fs55}If you get to talk to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.48,0:55:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉他 我们爱他 正在为他祈祷\N{\fs55}tell him that we love him and that we're praying for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.76,0:55:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为你们俩祈祷\N{\fs55}We're praying for both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.00,0:55:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我会的 再见\N{\fs55}I will. Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.36,0:55:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆 你简直疯了 你在发神经\N{\fs55}Tom,you're out of your mind, you're delirious.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.24,0:55:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我是疯了\N{\fs55}Of course,I'm out of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.84,0:55:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢 我就是疯子\N{\fs55}What do you think I am? I'm out of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.72,0:55:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你滚出去\N{\fs55}You leave this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.68,0:55:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆 不要 放下枪\N{\fs55}No,Tom! Put it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.32,0:55:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你滚开 臭娘们\N{\fs55}Get away from me,woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.88,0:56:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 我来关门吧\N{\fs55}I got that,sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.80,0:56:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,您好 需要帮忙吗\N{\fs55}May I help you,sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.32,0:56:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我想找马斯格罗夫准将谈谈\N{\fs55}I wish to speak to Brigadier General Musgrove.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.96,0:56:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没有提前预约 那是不可能的\N{\fs55}Not without an appointment you can't. That would be quite impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.44,0:56:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,能烦请您捎句话吗\N{\fs55}Uh,if you would kindly tell him
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.48,0:56:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就说托马斯·道斯下士想跟他说几句话\N{\fs55}Corporal Thomas Doss would appreciate a brief word.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.36,0:56:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他正在开一场非常重要的会议\N{\fs55}He's in a very important meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.44,0:56:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们曾在法国贝洛森林并肩作战 他是我的老队长\N{\fs55}I fought with him in France at Belleau Wood. He was my captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.12,0:56:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦您了 事关重大\N{\fs55}Please,ma'am,it's most vital.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.96,0:56:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您\N{\fs55}Thank you,ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.20,0:56:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,外面有一位叫托马斯·道斯的人\N{\fs55}There's a man out there,Tom Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.96,0:56:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,道斯吗\N{\fs55}Doss?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.40,0:57:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就能结束了\N{\fs55}Be over in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.60,0:57:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你就能毫发无损地回家了 就像什么都没发生\N{\fs55}You'll be home safe and sound, like nothing ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.44,0:57:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fs55}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.48,0:58:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是列兵戴斯蒙德·道斯一案的听证会\N{\fs55}This is a hearing into the matter of Private Desmond Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.72,0:58:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他被指控屡次违背直接命令\N{\fs55}The charge is disobeying a series of direct orders
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.36,0:58:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,无视指挥官\N{\fs55}from his commanding officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.64,0:58:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,被告的意见如何\N{\fs55}How says the defendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.52,0:58:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵道斯希望提出无罪抗辩\N{\fs55}Private Doss wishes to enter a "not guilty" plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.56,0:58:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵 是这样吗 我以为已经说好了\N{\fs55}Is that so,Private? I thought this was agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.72,0:58:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经想要接受认罪了\N{\fs55}You wanted to enter some sort of plea bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.96,0:58:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 长官 我改主意了 - 就这样变卦吗\N{\fs55}- Yes,sir,but I changed my mind. - Just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.56,0:58:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你想进行军事审判吗\N{\fs55}You wish to proceed to a court-martial?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.00,0:58:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 长官\N{\fs55}Yes,sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.56,0:58:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵 那如你所愿 进行审判吧\N{\fs55}Well,on your head,then,Private. Proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.08,0:58:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人 道斯向我们炫耀他的道德观念\N{\fs55}Your Honor,Private Doss waves his morality at us
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.36,0:58:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好像那是荣誉勋章一般\N{\fs55}like it's some kind of badge of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.56,0:58:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他不屑一顾 屡次违背直接命令\N{\fs55}He flaunts his contempt by directly disobeying a series of direct orders
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.32,0:58:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,无视指挥官\N{\fs55}from his commanding officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.64,0:58:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,与此同时 英勇的战士们却在浴血奋战\N{\fs55}When the very best of our young men are sacrificing their lives against...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.20,0:58:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你还好吗 - 还好\N{\fs55}- You okay? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.52,0:58:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,还在审吗\N{\fs55}Are they still deliberating?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.24,0:58:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs55}Yes,sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.52,0:59:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你把这封信带进去\N{\fs55}Okay,now you go take this in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.36,0:59:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我不行 只有军人才能进去\N{\fs55}I can't. It's strictly military personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.24,0:59:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那你让他们带进去\N{\fs55}Well,then you get one of them to take it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.72,0:59:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会帮忙的 他们都想置他于死地\N{\fs55}They ain't out to help. They're fixing to bury him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.08,0:59:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在军事法庭上 被告只需回答一个问题\N{\fs55}There is only one question that any military court need ask of the accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.60,0:59:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否否认 违背过萨斯顿上校的命令呢\N{\fs55}Do you deny disobeying Colonel Sangston's direct orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.24,0:59:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵 是不是呢\N{\fs55}Well,do you,Private?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.68,0:59:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不否认 - 那你要抗辩什么呢\N{\fs55}- No,sir. I don't. - Why are you contesting it,then?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.92,0:59:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你不想碰枪 那还有什么意义呢\N{\fs55}Why is it so important to you,given your refusal to even touch a weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.24,0:59:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么还要在战斗部队服役呢\N{\fs55}to serve in a combat unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.52,0:59:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因为日本偷袭珍珠港时 我能感同身受\N{\fs55}Because when the Japanese attacked Pearl Harbor,I took it personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.08,0:59:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识的每个人 都想奔赴战场 我也不例外\N{\fs55}Everyone I knew was on fire to join up,including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.68,0:59:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在我家乡 有两个人体检不合格\N{\fs55}There were two men in my home town... declared 4-F unfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.84,0:59:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因为不能参军 他们自杀了\N{\fs55}They killed themselves because they couldn't serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.40,1:00:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾在一家国防工厂工作 可以延迟服役\N{\fs55}I had a job in a defense plant and I could've taken a deferment,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.52,1:00:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但那是不对的\N{\fs55}but that ain't right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.32,1:00:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,只让同胞去浴血奋战 那是不对的\N{\fs55}It isn't right that other men should fight and die,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.76,1:00:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能坐享安宁\N{\fs55}that I would just be sitting at home safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.16,1:00:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要参军\N{\fs55}I need to serve.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.32,1:00:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我有精力和热情 去做一名军医\N{\fs55}I got the energy and the passion to serve as a medic.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.28,1:00:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,跟其他战士一同奋战 不避危险 只是...\N{\fs55}Right in the middle with the other guys. No less danger,just...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.00,1:00:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在大家夺取生命时 我要拯救生命\N{\fs55}While everybody else is taking life, I'm going to be saving it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.60,1:00:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,世界正在土崩瓦解\N{\fs55}With the world so set on tearing itself apart,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.88,1:00:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我这样的选择也不错\N{\fs55}it doesn't seem like such a bad thing to me
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.96,1:00:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我想尽一己之力 挽回这个世界\N{\fs55}to want to put a little bit of it back together.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.44,1:00:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 任何人不准进入...\N{\fs55}Sorry,sir,nobody's allowed to go...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.52,1:00:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你不懂 我的儿子是被告\N{\fs55}No,you don't understand. My son is the defendant.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.68,1:00:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 但任何人都不准许进入\N{\fs55}I understand,sir, but nobody's allowed...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.28,1:00:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我有重要信息 - 您不能进去...\N{\fs55}- I have information that's important. - Sir,you are not allowed...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.68,1:00:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然你的想法值得赞赏\N{\fs55}While the sentiments expressed are laudable,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.68,1:00:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但指控显然是成立的 所以...\N{\fs55}the facts of the charge seem incontestable,so...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.92,1:00:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,外面怎么回事\N{\fs55}What the hell is going on out there?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.80,1:01:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,让他进来\N{\fs55}Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.92,1:01:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是一战的军装 - 是的\N{\fs55}- That's a Great War uniform. - It is,sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.56,1:01:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要给您这封信\N{\fs55}Sir,I need to show you this.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.56,1:01:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言 您已经不是军人了\N{\fs55}With respect,sir,you are no longer a member of the military.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.76,1:01:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,您不能参加本次听证会 很抱歉\N{\fs55}You are unable to attend this hearing. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.72,1:01:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真是这样吗\N{\fs55}Is that truly the way it works,sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.84,1:01:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你为国家而战 失去了最珍贵的东西\N{\fs55}You fight for your country, you lose so much that was dear to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.20,1:01:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就算完了吗\N{\fs55}and then you're done with?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.20,1:01:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,旧军装被遗忘 就无权发言了\N{\fs55}The uniform is forgotten. You have no voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.28,1:01:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,您参加过佛兰德斯第四战役吗\N{\fs55}You were at Lys?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.60,1:01:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 还参加过贝洛森林之战\N{\fs55}I was,sir. And at Belleau Wood.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.88,1:01:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到 您两次被授勋\N{\fs55}Twice decorated,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.44,1:01:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 长官\N{\fs55}Yes,sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.40,1:01:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,想必您是这位列兵的父亲\N{\fs55}I take it you are the Private's father.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.92,1:01:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我叫托马斯·道斯\N{\fs55}I am,sir. Thomas Doss.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.88,1:01:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,作为一名老兵 你也知道有法律...\N{\fs55}Then,as a former military man, you know there are laws here...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.31,1:01:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道法律 也知道我的儿子会受法律保护\N{\fs55}Sir,I know the law and I know my son is protected by those laws.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.40,1:01:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,法律都是以宪法为基础的\N{\fs55}They are framed in our constitution.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.76,1:01:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信法律 跟他一样的\N{\fs55}And I believe in them,as he does.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.84,1:02:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因此我会去参战捍卫这些法律\N{\fs55}They are why I went and fought to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.20,1:02:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我当时是这样认为的\N{\fs55}At least,that is what I thought I was doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.44,1:02:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为如果不是这样的话\N{\fs55}Because if it wasn't for that,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.96,1:02:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那我都不知道 自己当时为何而战\N{\fs55}then I have no idea what the hell I was doing there,sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.72,1:02:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,道斯下士 谢谢\N{\fs55}Thank you,Corporal Doss.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.76,1:02:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,请把信给我吧\N{\fs55}Let me have the letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.96,1:02:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,您必须离开了\N{\fs55}You must go.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.96,1:02:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,被告是出于信仰拒服兵役者\N{\fs55}The defendant's rights as a conscientious objector
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.64,1:02:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,其权力受到国会法案保护\N{\fs55}are protected by an Act of Congress
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.76,1:02:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不能被强制放弃那些权力\N{\fs55}and he cannot be compelled to waive those rights.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.68,1:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,包括本案中拒绝持枪的权力\N{\fs55}That includes,in this case, his disobeying orders to bear arms.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.28,1:02:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,落款 战争服务指挥官马斯格罗夫准将 于华盛顿特区\N{\fs55}Signed,Brigadier General Musgrove, War Services Commander,Washington,D.C.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.76,1:02:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,上校\N{\fs55}Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.32,1:03:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我撤回指控 - 那就可以结案了\N{\fs55}- I withdraw the charges,sir. - Then this case is dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.84,1:03:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,道斯 你可以走上充满硝烟的战场\N{\fs55}Private Doss,you are free to run into the hellfire of battle
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.24,1:03:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可以不持枪保卫自己\N{\fs55}without a single weapon to protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.96,1:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以继续履行职责 受训成为一名战地医务兵\N{\fs55}You may resume your duties and begin training as a combat medic.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.40,1:03:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他在哪 - 直接就走了\N{\fs55}- Where is he? - Gone. Straight after.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.64,1:03:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我让他留下来 说你肯定想见他\N{\fs55}I begged him to stay. I told him you'd want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.56,1:03:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 我明白\N{\fs55}No,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.76,1:03:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你回家后 告诉他 我爱他\N{\fs55}When you get home, you tell him I love him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.76,1:03:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs55}Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.04,1:04:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要回来\N{\fs55}You better come home to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.42,1:04:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\fs85\bord0\shad0\c&HF3FDEF&\pos(434.8,923.509)}1945年5月 冲绳
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.52,1:04:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好莱坞 闭嘴吧\N{\fs55}Hollywood,shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.08,1:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,别唱了 闭嘴\N{\fs55}Come on,pipe down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.60,1:04:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 闭嘴 - 别唱了\N{\fs55}- Shut up,man. - Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.40,1:04:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好莱坞 我发誓 我要崩了你\N{\fs55}I swear to God, Hollywood,I will shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.56,1:04:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,往嘴里塞只袜子吧 到战场再嚎吧\N{\fs55}Put a sock in it,will you? Save the crowing for when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.76,1:04:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真扫兴\N{\fs55}Killjoy was here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.96,1:04:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,让开\N{\fs55}Give him room.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.28,1:04:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,注意 靠边站\N{\fs55}Clear! Clear! Move aside!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.56,1:05:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是96步兵师 只剩这些人了\N{\fs55}The 96th... or what's left of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.04,1:05:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就是要接替他们\N{\fs55}These are the guys we're replacing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.20,1:06:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我这里安全 - 没人\N{\fs55}- Seems good to me. - Clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.56,1:06:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 都没人 - 安全\N{\fs55}- As gold. - Clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.88,1:06:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,中士 这里安全\N{\fs55}All clear,Sarge!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.72,1:06:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是格洛弗上尉\N{\fs55}Captain Glover.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.56,1:06:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,第96步兵师 Manville中尉\N{\fs55}Lieutenant Manville,96th.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.80,1:06:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被分派给您了 长官\N{\fs55}We've been assigned to you,sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.76,1:06:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs55}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.48,1:06:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 给他们点吃的 - 是的 长官\N{\fs55}- Let's get these men some chow. - Yes,sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.60,1:06:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这是豪威尔中士\N{\fs55}This is,uh,Sergeant Howell.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.04,1:06:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很高兴见到您 - 坐下吧\N{\fs55}- Good to meet you,sir. - Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.40,1:06:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哪位是道斯呢\N{\fs55}Who's Doss?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.92,1:06:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那边\N{\fs55}Over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.48,1:07:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你是道斯吗\N{\fs55}You Doss?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.28,1:07:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我是欧文·谢克特\N{\fs55}Irv Schecter.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.12,1:07:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,咱俩和佩奇是这里仅剩的医务兵了\N{\fs55}You,and me and Page here are about the only medics we got left in this area.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.44,1:07:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可能要一起作战了\N{\fs55}So,I guess we're gonna be working together.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.08,1:07:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚从前线下来吗\N{\fs55}You just come off the line?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.96,1:07:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那边怎么样\N{\fs55}What's it like?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.60,1:07:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我在问你 前线什么样\N{\fs55}I said,What's it like?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.72,1:07:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,钢锯岭\N{\fs55}Hacksaw.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.52,1:07:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们攀登过六次 六次都被打下来了\N{\fs55}We climbed up six times. Six times,they threw us off.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.84,1:07:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一次时 96步兵师基本全军覆没\N{\fs55}Last time,there wasn't anything left of the 96th.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.80,1:07:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是禽兽\N{\fs55}They're animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.12,1:07:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的禽兽\N{\fs55}Stinking animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.12,1:07:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,日本人不顾自己的死活\N{\fs55}Nips don't care if they live or die.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.56,1:07:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想死 不断向我们涌来\N{\fs55}They want to die. They keep coming at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.64,1:08:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他们不会放弃\N{\fs55}And they ain't never going to give up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.12,1:08:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,永远不会\N{\fs55}Never.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.84,1:08:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哥们 给你\N{\fs55}Here. Hey,buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.28,1:08:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,日本人专打伤员\N{\fs55}The Japs deliberately target the wounded.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.48,1:08:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,摘掉所有红十字标志吧\N{\fs55}Lose all your Red Cross markings.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.56,1:08:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他们打死医务兵会有奖励\N{\fs55}Nips put a premium on shooting medics.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.76,1:08:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,白色袖标就是活靶子\N{\fs55}The white is a bull's-eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.80,1:08:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,给你一顶新头盔\N{\fs55}Here,I got you a new helmet.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.84,1:08:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,均码的\N{\fs55}One size fits all.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.60,1:08:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的目标 钢锯岭\N{\fs55}That's our objective. Hacksaw Ridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.76,1:08:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,攻下这里 也许就能攻下冲绳\N{\fs55}We take it,maybe we get Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.48,1:08:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,攻下冲绳 就能攻下日本\N{\fs55}We get Okinawa,we take Japan.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.60,1:08:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一会 让海军先给他们一点颜色看看\N{\fs55}Take a breather. Our pals in the Navy are going to soften them up for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.20,1:09:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这样狂轰乱炸 没人能活下来\N{\fs55}Nobody can survive that shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.60,1:09:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他们可以\N{\fs55}Oh,but they can.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.12,1:09:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉 这仨碉堡的位置准确吗\N{\fs55}Lieutenant,these bunkers here, here and here,is that accurate?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.44,1:09:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 有三个...\N{\fs55}Yeah,there's three...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.52,1:09:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 可能稍微靠后 但这是全部了\N{\fs55}Yes,sir,maybe a little further back, but it's all...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.48,1:10:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,上面完全不同\N{\fs55}It's all different up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.60,1:10:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了 上尉\N{\fs55}All clear,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.76,1:10:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟们 出发了\N{\fs55}Gents,move out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.64,1:10:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是血\N{\fs55}It's blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.36,1:10:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,别废话\N{\fs55}No shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.48,1:10:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是在堪萨斯了\N{\fs55}We're not in Kansas anymore,Dorothy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.80,1:10:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,继续爬吧\N{\fs55}Keep climbing.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.64,1:10:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 我拉你\N{\fs55}Here,come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.60,1:11:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们过去 让一下\N{\fs55}Coming through,make way. Out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.60,1:11:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 布朗 - 怎么\N{\fs55}- Brown. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.88,1:11:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,给杰索普\N{\fs55}Give this to Jessop.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.04,1:11:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,下士\N{\fs55}Corporal!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.44,1:13:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有敌人\N{\fs55}Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.88,1:13:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,卧倒\N{\fs55}Get down!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.84,1:13:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下\N{\fs55}Get down!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.08,1:13:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在哪 什么都看不到\N{\fs55}Where the hell are they? I can't see nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.96,1:13:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我也不知道 - 他们在哪...\N{\fs55}- Beats me,pal. - Where the...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.48,1:13:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,医务兵\N{\fs55}Medic!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.04,1:13:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这边\N{\fs55}We're over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.44,1:13:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克 把手按在这里\N{\fs55}Put your hand right here. Put your hand on there,Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.80,1:13:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fs55}Come on,come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.68,1:14:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 我们给你找掩护 跟我过来\N{\fs55}Come on,we're going to get you under cover. Come on,come with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.32,1:14:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克 跟我过来\N{\fs55}Come with me,Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.56,1:14:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,继续前进 前进\N{\fs55}Keep moving forward! Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.84,1:14:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都看不见\N{\fs55}I can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.20,1:14:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是吗 - 我不知道 反正开枪吧\N{\fs55}- Is that one? - I don't know. Just shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.48,1:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 走吧\N{\fs55}All right,let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.76,1:14:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,维托\N{\fs55}Vito!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.60,1:14:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fs55}Oh,shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.16,1:15:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 医务兵 维托受伤了 - 我来了\N{\fs55}- Medic! Vito's down! - I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.72,1:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我来了\N{\fs55}Okay. I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.96,1:15:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,闪开\N{\fs55}Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.56,1:15:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你受伤了吗\N{\fs55}You hurt?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.28,1:15:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\fs55}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.68,1:16:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,拉尔夫 我来了 深呼吸\N{\fs55}Come on,I got you,Ralph. Just breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.04,1:16:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,拉尔夫 深呼吸 没事了\N{\fs55}Just breathe. Just breathe,Ralph. It's okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.36,1:16:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,拉尔夫 调整呼吸\N{\fs55}Just breathe,Ralph,just breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.60,1:16:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我在呢 没事了\N{\fs55}I got you,I got you. I got you. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.64,1:16:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,打一针吗啡 继续救人\N{\fs55}Hey! Hey! Give him a shot of morphine and move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.16,1:16:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他活不过今天了\N{\fs55}He's not going to last a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.64,1:16:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,道斯 求你了 别走啊\N{\fs55}Please. Please,Doss,no. No. Don't leave me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.08,1:16:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 别放弃我\N{\fs55}Don't leave me. God,please don't leave me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.64,1:16:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我家里还有孩子\N{\fs55}I've got kids!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.64,1:16:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了 救救我\N{\fs55}Please. Please,don't. Please,don't leave me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.76,1:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪也不去 我会带你回家的\N{\fs55}I ain't going anywhere. I'm going to get you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.84,1:16:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,拉尔夫 我不会走的 我会带你回家第\N{\fs55}I got you,Ralph. Okay? I'm going to get you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.76,1:16:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,给你打一针吗啡\N{\fs55}Here comes the morphine. Here comes the morphine.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.96,1:17:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,拉尔夫 你马上就不疼了\N{\fs55}It's going to kick in real quick,Ralph.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.60,1:17:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就把你转移下去\N{\fs55}We're going to get you shifted.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.72,1:17:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,担架\N{\fs55}Stretcher! Stretcher!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.60,1:17:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 站起来 前进 - 不行 我受伤了\N{\fs55}- Get up. Keep moving,son. - I can't,I'm wounded.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.76,1:17:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么事都没有\N{\fs55}There's nothing wrong with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.00,1:17:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 坚持住\N{\fs55}Shit! Hang on,kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.64,1:17:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快走 不动就是等死\N{\fs55}Move. A sitting duck's a dead one.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.88,1:17:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\fs55}Move. Go,go,go!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.00,1:17:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他需要优先救治\N{\fs55}This guy's a priority.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.92,1:17:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我们吧 放这吧\N{\fs55}We got him,we got him. Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.68,1:17:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,优先救治吗 没学过分诊吗 他撑不到送下去的\N{\fs55}A priority? You ever heard of triage? He'll be dead before we get him down.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.96,1:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道\N{\fs55}You don't know that!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.36,1:17:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,送他下去 好吗\N{\fs55}Get him down. All right? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.20,1:17:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 走吧 - 好的\N{\fs55}- Okay. Okay. Go. - Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.04,1:17:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了 马上送你回家\N{\fs55}It's all right,buddy. We're going to get you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.08,1:17:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,医务兵 救命啊\N{\fs55}Medic! Help! Help.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.72,1:18:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们看不见他们 他们也看不见我们\N{\fs55}I figure if we can't see them, then they can't see us neither.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.20,1:18:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克 我来了 你哪受伤了\N{\fs55}I got you,Frank. Where you hit?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.92,1:18:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 傻子 好像他们看得见 - 道斯 快走\N{\fs55}- I think they can see us,smart ass! - Doss,come on,come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.16,1:18:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我一把\N{\fs55}Give me a hand here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.04,1:18:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,蹲下 长官\N{\fs55}Get down,sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.80,1:18:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,碉堡就在那里\N{\fs55}Over there! The bunkers.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.20,1:18:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见了 最好卧倒\N{\fs55}I see them. Better stay down,sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.80,1:18:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我看见了 在正前方 - 我也看见了\N{\fs55}- I got 'em,dead ahead. - Yeah,I see 'em,too.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.40,1:18:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,尽量逼近 全火力压制\N{\fs55}Push in as close as you can. Give them everything you've got.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.68,1:18:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我派炸药组 包抄他们\N{\fs55}I'll send in the weapons team to flank them.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.72,1:19:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住 你会没事的 好吗\N{\fs55}You keep that tight,you're going to be right as rain. All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.04,1:19:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,道斯 交给我吧\N{\fs55}I got him,Doss. I got him.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.88,1:19:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fs55}You doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.20,1:19:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好\N{\fs55}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.40,1:19:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,准备 发射\N{\fs55}And,fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.68,1:19:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下\N{\fs55}Down!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.88,1:19:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的\N{\fs55}Son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.84,1:19:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你过去 - 好的\N{\fs55}- You,get on it. - Yes,sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.84,1:19:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 开枪\N{\fs55}Take 'em. Go. Fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.56,1:20:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护\N{\fs55}Cover!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.24,1:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,食尸鬼 冲上去 躲到弹坑里\N{\fs55}Go,go. Go,Ghoul. Get in the hole. Stay there.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.12,1:20:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,史密提 快去 我们掩护 大步跨过去\N{\fs55}Go! Go,Smitty, we'll cover you. Leapfrog.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.96,1:20:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护\N{\fs55}Cover.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.92,1:20:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,炸药包\N{\fs55}Satchel!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.92,1:20:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 食尸鬼 - 安全\N{\fs55}- Ghoul! - Clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.36,1:20:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,食尸鬼 坚持住\N{\fs55}Come on,stick it. Stick it,Ghoul.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.28,1:20:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护\N{\fs55}Cover! Cover!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.08,1:21:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fs55}Son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.60,1:21:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护\N{\fs55}Cover his ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.44,1:21:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,医务兵 救命\N{\fs55}Medic! Medic! Help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.56,1:21:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,冲啊\N{\fs55}Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.12,1:22:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,医务兵\N{\fs55}Medic!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.00,1:22:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了 把手按在这里\N{\fs55}I'm here. Put your hand on it. Put your hand on it!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.24,1:23:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快冲\N{\fs55}Go,go,go!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.60,1:23:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,食尸鬼\N{\fs55}Ghoul. Ghoul.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.28,1:23:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了 你哪受伤了\N{\fs55}You're okay. Where you hit?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.72,1:23:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你的脑袋磕了一下 没事的\N{\fs55}You got a bump on the head,that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.48,1:23:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么\N{\fs55}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.04,1:23:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 安迪 - 全名是什么\N{\fs55}- Andy. - Andy what?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.08,1:23:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪·沃克\N{\fs55}Andy Walker.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.56,1:23:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,外号是什么\N{\fs55}Also known as?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.44,1:23:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,食尸鬼\N{\fs55}Ghoul.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.84,1:23:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,食尸鬼 你没事的\N{\fs55}Ghoul. Ghoul,you're okay,you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.76,1:24:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,干得好 兄弟们\N{\fs55}Good job,men. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.04,1:24:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,挖好战壕过夜 守住这里\N{\fs55}Dig in for the night. We hold this spot,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.64,1:24:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,明天就能拿下整个钢锯岭\N{\fs55}we mop up the rest of the ridge tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.96,1:24:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们 在碉堡里面或附近 给自己选好位置\N{\fs55}Okay,boys. Find yourself a nice safe hole in or near the bunker.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.56,1:24:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,每两小时换班守夜\N{\fs55}Rotate watch every two hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.56,1:24:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道外面有什么情况 脑袋和屁股都放低\N{\fs55}We don't know what's out there. Heads down,asses lower.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.72,1:24:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不说英语的 一律格杀勿论\N{\fs55}And shoot anything that don't speak English.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.60,1:24:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 也包括格里瑟吗 中士 - 尤其是他\N{\fs55}- Does that include Grease,Sarge? - Particularly him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.40,1:24:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你是要去方便 还是什么的\N{\fs55}I don't care if you need to take a piss or a dump,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.76,1:24:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人出去都很危险\N{\fs55}it ain't safe to go out there alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.44,1:24:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你还要去哪 道斯\N{\fs55}Where the hell are you going,Doss?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.48,1:24:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,外面还有很多伤员 中士\N{\fs55}Still more wounded out there,Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.72,1:24:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他一起去\N{\fs55}I'll go with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.44,1:24:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要眼观六路 耳听八方\N{\fs55}Be smart. Keep your ears down.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.36,1:24:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 各自找地方吧\N{\fs55}All right,let's find a spot.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.48,1:24:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinnelli和Henry在前15分钟就直接死了\N{\fs55}Rinnelli and Henry dead in the first 15 minutes,just straight off.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.32,1:25:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,直接就死了\N{\fs55}Straight off.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.64,1:25:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,还有大眼睛彼得森 以及斯坦福和墨菲\N{\fs55}Peterson,Popeye. Standford and Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.60,1:25:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,佩奇和昂格尔\N{\fs55}Page and Unger.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.48,1:25:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,罗尔斯顿\N{\fs55}Ralston.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.44,1:25:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,和平年代 黑发人送白发人\N{\fs55}"In peace,sons bury their fathers,"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.11,1:25:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,战争年代 白发人送黑发人\N{\fs55}"in war,fathers bury their sons."
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.32,1:25:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,别再唠叨那些废话了\N{\fs55}You wanna stop spouting that crap,huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.44,1:25:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,说那些有什么用呢\N{\fs55}It don't help none.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.28,1:25:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 没错 在这确实没用\N{\fs55}Yeah,you got that right. Not here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.00,1:25:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,给我吧\N{\fs55}give me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.20,1:25:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这名伤员腹部受伤了\N{\fs55}Hey,we've got an abdominal wound.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.96,1:25:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他需要输一点血\N{\fs55}This man is going to need some plasma.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.24,1:25:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没问题 - 交给我们吧\N{\fs55}- You got it. - Leave him with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.68,1:25:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 你没事了 他们会救你的\N{\fs55}Okay. You're okay now. They got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.16,1:26:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要找一个洞来栖身\N{\fs55}Should we find a hole and dig in?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.48,1:26:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好主意\N{\fs55}Sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.20,1:26:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,戴上头盔\N{\fs55}Put your helmet on.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.40,1:26:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你不吃吗\N{\fs55}You ain't going to eat them?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.56,1:26:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不吃肉 你吃吧\N{\fs55}I don't eat meat. Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.52,1:26:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你当然不吃肉了\N{\fs55}Of course you don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.92,1:26:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,她真挺漂亮的\N{\fs55}That's one heck of a dame.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.76,1:26:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样的 通常很难追到她 你知道吧\N{\fs55}You know you're fighting out of your weight class with her,don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.88,1:26:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我知道\N{\fs55}Yes,I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.24,1:26:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,别告诉她\N{\fs55}Don't tell her that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.96,1:26:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我这样的男人在一起 她会更幸福\N{\fs55}She'd be much happier with a man like me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.03,1:26:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 直到她了解你\N{\fs55}Yeah,until she got to know you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.76,1:27:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我偶尔挺混蛋的\N{\fs55}I'm an asshole sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.28,1:27:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只是偶尔吗\N{\fs55}Sometimes?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.80,1:27:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,行吧 有你的\N{\fs55}Yeah,all right. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.00,1:27:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这些日本人太狡猾了\N{\fs55}These Japs are sneaky.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.24,1:27:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我先去放哨吧 你休息一会\N{\fs55}I'll take first watch,all right? You get some shut-eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.72,1:28:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,做恶梦啦\N{\fs55}Hell of a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.96,1:28:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,梦到我被刺穿了 但什么都做不了\N{\fs55}Dreamed I got myself skewered. I couldn't do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.64,1:28:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,步枪就在这\N{\fs55}Rifle's just there.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.88,1:29:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,枪不会咬人的\N{\fs55}It won't bite.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.72,1:29:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它会的\N{\fs55}Yeah,it will.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.08,1:29:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你周围\N{\fs55}Look around you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.56,1:29:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,经历过今天的场面\N{\fs55}After what we've just been through,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.92,1:29:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,任何正常的人都会想找武器的\N{\fs55}any sane man would be screaming for a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.04,1:29:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我没说过我是正常的\N{\fs55}I never claimed to be sane.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.00,1:29:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸是酒鬼\N{\fs55}My daddy's a drunk.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.08,1:29:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他早就想戒酒 但是一直戒不掉\N{\fs55}He fought it for years, but it kind of got a hold of him hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.12,1:29:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这让他变得很刻薄\N{\fs55}Made him mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.36,1:29:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,至少你知道你爸是谁\N{\fs55}Least you knew him.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.72,1:29:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不知道我爸是谁 我也懒得知道\N{\fs55}Mine could have been any one of 10 guys, and none of them worth a damn,so...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.84,1:29:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你是妈妈养大的\N{\fs55}So,your momma raised you?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.48,1:29:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识她 但我五岁时 就被她扔进孤儿院了\N{\fs55}I knew her,but she gave me to an orphanage when I was five.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.64,1:29:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,后来再没见过她\N{\fs55}Never saw her again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.08,1:29:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我学会了恨\N{\fs55}I learned how to hate quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.24,1:29:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,学会了快速识人 但我却看错你了\N{\fs55}I learned how to judge people quicker, and I got you very wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.24,1:30:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸以前总打我和我哥 无缘无故\N{\fs55}My daddy used to beat me and my brother just because the sun rose,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.24,1:30:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,莫名其妙 就打一顿\N{\fs55}and then whip us just because it set.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.92,1:30:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这些我都可以忍受\N{\fs55}I could take that...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.56,1:30:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但他打我妈妈的时候...\N{\fs55}...but when he would do it to our momma...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.00,1:30:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你滚开 臭娘们\N{\fs55}Get away from me,woman!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.60,1:30:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你够了 停手吧 听见了吗\N{\fs55}That's enough. No more. Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.88,1:30:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你开枪吧\N{\fs55}Pull the damn trigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.80,1:30:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊 快住手\N{\fs55}Stop it! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.44,1:30:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但你没有杀他吗\N{\fs55}But you didn't kill him?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.44,1:30:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在我心里 我已经杀死他了\N{\fs55}In my heart,I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.88,1:31:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我向上帝发誓\N{\fs55}So that's why I made my promise to God,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.80,1:31:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也不碰枪了\N{\fs55}I ain't never going to touch a gun again.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.64,1:31:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我的枪不会给你 你这疯子\N{\fs55}Well,I ain't giving you mine, 'cause you're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.24,1:31:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fs55}Son of a...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.08,1:31:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的\N{\fs55}Son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.20,1:32:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑 快撤回这里来\N{\fs55}Move,move! Get your asses over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.40,1:32:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,快走啊\N{\fs55}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.32,1:32:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退 快跑\N{\fs55}Fall back,fall back! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.60,1:33:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是从地下冒出来的\N{\fs55}They're coming from underground.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.08,1:33:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,探照灯 这里是B6 请求立即支援\N{\fs55}Searchlight,this is Baker Six. Request immediate support.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.76,1:33:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,目标为YT515\N{\fs55}Target is Yoke-Tare-Five-One-Five.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.72,1:33:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我知道我们在这鬼地方\N{\fs55}Yes! Yes,I know that's where the hell we are,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.76,1:33:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但我估计快挺不住了\N{\fs55}but I don't expect to be here much longer!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.12,1:33:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我请求炮火支援了\N{\fs55}I called an artillery strike.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.80,1:33:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退 快点\N{\fs55}Fall back. Move. Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.96,1:33:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退 有敌人\N{\fs55}Fall back! Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.44,1:33:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计 我在这\N{\fs55}Hey,buddy. I'm right here. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.60,1:34:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs55}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.68,1:34:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护我\N{\fs55}Cover me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.84,1:34:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\fs55}Go,go!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.36,1:34:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快走啊 孩子\N{\fs55}Get out of here,kid!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.16,1:34:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 孩子\N{\fs55}Come here,son.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.92,1:34:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道怎么做 按住了\N{\fs55}You know what to do. Keep pressure on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.32,1:34:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不用 我不要血浆 给他吧\N{\fs55}No! Don't need plasma. Give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.80,1:34:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里 我没事 快去吧\N{\fs55}Over there. I'll be okay. Go. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.08,1:34:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,格里瑟 带欧文回去\N{\fs55}Grease! Get Irv's back.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.84,1:34:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 交给我吧 - 一会见\N{\fs55}- You got it,okay. - See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.96,1:34:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 走了\N{\fs55}Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.88,1:35:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得抓紧走了 快点\N{\fs55}We gotta move right now. Come on,come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.44,1:35:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\fs55}Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.20,1:35:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,敌军太多 立即撤退\N{\fs55}There's too many, get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.00,1:35:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,快撤\N{\fs55}Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.84,1:36:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我好害怕 - 这能止痛\N{\fs55}- I'm scared. I'm scared. - It's going to help the pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.72,1:36:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样 振作一点\N{\fs55}No,don't. Don't you do that. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.04,1:36:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,史密提 坚持住 我背你走\N{\fs55}Come on,Smitty,you stay with me. Let's go. We gotta move.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.56,1:37:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我把他放下来 帮把手\N{\fs55}Help me get him down. Help me get him down.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.04,1:37:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs55}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.60,1:37:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 带他走\N{\fs55}Come on,let's move. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.12,1:37:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计 帮不了他了 他已经死了\N{\fs55}Can't help him,buddy,he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.16,1:37:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 - 走吧 离开这里\N{\fs55}- No. - Come on! We gotta get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.60,1:37:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,快撤\N{\fs55}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.12,1:37:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 所有人都撤\N{\fs55}Come on. Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.88,1:37:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,撤离钢锯岭\N{\fs55}Off the ridge!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.40,1:38:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要我怎么做\N{\fs55}What is it you want of me?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.60,1:38:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fs55}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.52,1:38:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我听不见你的声音\N{\fs55}I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.56,1:38:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,医务兵 救救我\N{\fs55}Medic,help me! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.92,1:38:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我\N{\fs55}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.44,1:38:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,救我 上帝啊\N{\fs55}Help me,Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.20,1:38:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs55}All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.20,1:39:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事了 放轻松\N{\fs55}You're in good hands. Easy does it. Easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.32,1:39:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,六...八...\N{\fs55}...six... eight...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.48,1:39:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,十四\N{\fs55}Fourteen.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.04,1:39:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧确保他们安全\N{\fs55}Get these men secured immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.68,1:39:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 长官\N{\fs55}Yes,sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.92,1:39:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 列兵Ford 有多少人 - 只下来32个 长官\N{\fs55}- Private Ford,how many? - Thirty-two only came down,sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.68,1:39:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\N{\fs55}Good Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.88,1:39:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把伤员装上车 - 遵命 长官\N{\fs55}- Let's load 'em up. - Yes,sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.92,1:40:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哈里 我是戴斯蒙\N{\fs55}Harry. It's Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.52,1:40:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你会没事的 保持呼吸就好\N{\fs55}We going to fix you up. You just got to keep breathing. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.40,1:40:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 上校要见你 长官 - 我需要你的吉普车\N{\fs55}- Colonel wants to see you,sir. - I need your jeep.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.16,1:40:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在这放哨 盯好日本人\N{\fs55}You two stay here,keep watch, keep your eyes peeled for Japs.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.76,1:40:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是... - 留在这里盯紧了\N{\fs55}- No,but... - Stay here! Keep watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.40,1:40:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 遵命 长官 - 遵命 长官\N{\fs55}- Yes,sir. - Yes,sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.68,1:40:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我\N{\fs55}Help. Help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.56,1:40:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 我来了\N{\fs55}Watch out. I got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.52,1:40:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,手放在这 按住了\N{\fs55}Put your hand on it. Keep pressure on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.72,1:40:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我会回来的 好吗 - 好\N{\fs55}- I'm comin' back. Okay? - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.12,1:41:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,别急 慢一点\N{\fs55}Easy,fellas,easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.96,1:41:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,抬下来\N{\fs55}Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.60,1:41:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,抬下来 数三下 一 二 三\N{\fs55}Okay,guys,let's go. On the count of three. One,two,three.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.76,1:41:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,求助 医务兵过来\N{\fs55}Help,medic over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.00,1:41:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了 坚持住 伙计\N{\fs55}It's okay,buddy,hold it together.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.04,1:41:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到崖边了 埃里克\N{\fs55}We're at the edge,Eric.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.12,1:41:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,坐好了 好吗\N{\fs55}You just sit tight,okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.16,1:41:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,埃里克 没事的 你会没事的\N{\fs55}You're okay,Eric. You're okay,buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.76,1:41:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 这应该没问题\N{\fs55}Son of a gun,this is going to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.08,1:41:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一条腿套一个结 埃里克\N{\fs55}One for each leg,Eric.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.12,1:42:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你套好绳子 就带你下去\N{\fs55}We're going to get you dressed up in a jiffy and get you down.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.20,1:42:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有我在\N{\fs55}I got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.56,1:42:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有我在呢 埃里克\N{\fs55}I got you now,Eric.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.44,1:42:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你要相信我 埃里克\N{\fs55}You have to trust me now,Eric. You're gonna have to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.08,1:42:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,日本鬼子\N{\fs55}Japs!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.36,1:42:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 是自己人 快去\N{\fs55}Hold on,one of ours. Hold on! Let's go,let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.40,1:42:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,有我在\N{\fs55}I got you. I got you. I got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.72,1:42:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有我在的 你会没事的\N{\fs55}Come on,I got you. You're okay. You're okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.92,1:42:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,, 汉克 又一个\N{\fs55}Hank,another one.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.76,1:43:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,上校 停止炮击钢锯岭\N{\fs55}Colonel,call off the artillery attack on Hacksaw.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.12,1:43:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不能炮击 我军还有一百多人在上面\N{\fs55}Couldn't call it in. There's still over 100 men left up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.60,1:43:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们停止炮击钢锯岭\N{\fs55}Tell them to call off the artillery on Hacksaw.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.88,1:43:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克 坐下 给你拿杯水\N{\fs55}Sit down,Jack. I'll get you a drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.88,1:43:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们失去掩护了\N{\fs55}We just lost our cover.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.00,1:43:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他们来了 我们快撤\N{\fs55}They're stirrin', we got to move. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.60,1:43:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,来得正好 一直有人下来\N{\fs55}About time. They just keep coming by the...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.24,1:43:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 抬起来 - 来了\N{\fs55}- OK,OK. Pick it up. - I got this.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.68,1:44:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,道斯\N{\fs55}Doss. Doss.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.76,1:44:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我\N{\fs55}Help. Help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.44,1:44:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 深吸口气\N{\fs55}You're gonna have to trust me. Take a breath.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.04,1:45:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走 伙计\N{\fs55}Let's go,buddy. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.40,1:45:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克 你不知道上面的人是死是活\N{\fs55}Jack,you don't know if your men up there are dead or alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.12,1:45:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没有支援 不能再上去了\N{\fs55}You can't go back up there without reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.48,1:45:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,否则就是去送死\N{\fs55}You'll end up killing the rest of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.60,1:45:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那就给我援兵\N{\fs55}Then give me the reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.68,1:46:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有人了 已经没有援军了\N{\fs55}I don't have any fresh men,okay? I don't have any troops.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.52,1:46:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,今天有三个营的人都牺牲了\N{\fs55}Three battalions got wiped out today.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.68,1:46:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,调配援军至少需要一天\N{\fs55}It'll take more than a day to get men in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.44,1:46:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我等不了那么久\N{\fs55}I need them faster than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.92,1:48:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fs55}It's okay,it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.80,1:48:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\fs55}It's all right. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.12,1:48:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的\N{\fs55}Everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.68,1:48:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是吗啡 是好东西\N{\fs55}Morphine. It's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.84,1:48:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,安静\N{\fs55}Shh.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.36,1:49:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,平尼克 我是道斯\N{\fs55}Pinnick,Pinnick. Pinnick. It's Doss.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.24,1:49:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,安静 我来帮你\N{\fs55}It's Doss. Be quiet. Be quiet. I got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.88,1:49:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 中弹了吗 - 我看不见了\N{\fs55}- Are you hit? - Yeah. I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.96,1:49:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,安静 小点声\N{\fs55}Be quiet. Just be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.84,1:49:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不要动 在我在 坚持住\N{\fs55}Hold still now. I got you. Hold tight.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.72,1:49:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 睁开眼试试\N{\fs55}There you go. Try now. Try now.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.12,1:49:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为自己瞎了\N{\fs55}I thought I was blind!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.40,1:49:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小点声 能走路吗\N{\fs55}Shh... Keep it down. Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.92,1:49:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fs55}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.32,1:49:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们离开这里 走吧\N{\fs55}We got to get out of here,okay? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.84,1:49:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 接到你了\N{\fs55}Good. Okay,we got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.48,1:49:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我们吧\N{\fs55}We got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.48,1:50:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,特德\N{\fs55}Hey,Ted.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.32,1:50:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我是戴斯蒙 我来帮你\N{\fs55}It's me,it's Desmond. I'm gonna fix you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.48,1:50:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 准备好离开这了吗 - 当然\N{\fs55}- You ready to get out of here? - Sure am.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.32,1:50:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,主啊 请帮助我再救一人\N{\fs55}Please,Lord,help me get one more.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.52,1:50:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,再多救一个人\N{\fs55}Help me get one more.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.88,1:51:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了 帮助我再多救一个\N{\fs55}Please,help me get one more.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.96,1:51:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,再多救一个 帮我再救一人\N{\fs55}One more. Help me get one more.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.12,1:51:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,再救一人 帮我再救一人\N{\fs55}One more. Help me get one more.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.36,1:51:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,再救一人\N{\fs55}One more.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.48,1:51:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,让一让\N{\fs55}Coming through.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.60,1:51:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这些家伙哪来的\N{\fs55}Where the hell are these guys coming from?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.48,1:52:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,钢锯岭\N{\fs55}From Hacksaw.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.72,1:52:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我以为他们全撤退了 - 没全部撤退\N{\fs55}- I thought they pulled out. - Not all of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.52,1:52:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,上面有一个疯子 不断送伤员下来\N{\fs55}Some nut's up there dragging wounded from the top.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.52,1:52:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至还送下来几个日本佬\N{\fs55}Even lowered a couple of Japs.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.36,1:52:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没挺过来 我过一会回来\N{\fs55}They didn't make it. Back with you directly.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.20,1:52:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,轻点 准备好了 出发\N{\fs55}Easy,easy. All set,move out.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.04,1:52:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,快过来 到处都是日本兵\N{\fs55}Get in here. There's Nips everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.64,1:52:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼 玉米秆列兵\N{\fs55}Son of a bitch. Private Corn Stalk.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.36,1:52:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你真让人惊讶\N{\fs55}You are nothing if not full of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.48,1:52:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你要吗啡吗\N{\fs55}You want some morphine?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.40,1:53:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 当然 或者给我一枪 - 好的\N{\fs55}- Hell,yes. That or a bullet. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.28,1:53:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs55}There. There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.24,1:53:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 让我看看\N{\fs55}All right,let me see. Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.68,1:53:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这里怎么样 还可以\N{\fs55}How's this doing? Okay,not bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.32,1:53:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看\N{\fs55}Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.36,1:53:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没有看上去那么糟\N{\fs55}It looks much worse than it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.96,1:53:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩们还是会想吻你的\N{\fs55}Girls will still want to kiss you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.40,1:53:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,中士 你先等一会 好吗\N{\fs55}Sarge,you okay here for a while?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.68,1:53:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 快走吧\N{\fs55}Yeah,fine. Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.96,1:53:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我会回来的\N{\fs55}I'm coming back.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.68,1:53:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗 我们走吧\N{\fs55}You ready? Let's go. You and me,come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.72,1:54:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉 你一定得来看看\N{\fs55}Captain. There's something you gotta see.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.96,1:54:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,一整夜 我们的人不断被运下来\N{\fs55}Our guys have been coming down in droves all night.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.32,1:54:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好莱坞也下来了 我以为再也见不到他了\N{\fs55}And Hollywood's here. I never thought I'd see that guy again.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.76,1:54:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来 他就在这边\N{\fs55}Come on,follow me. He's right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.24,1:54:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这究竟是什么情况\N{\fs55}What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.44,1:54:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗 长官\N{\fs55}How you doing,sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.00,1:54:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊 上尉\N{\fs55}Hey,Cap.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.44,1:54:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉\N{\fs55}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.00,1:54:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 见到你真好 孩子 - 格洛弗上尉\N{\fs55}- It's good to see you,kid. - Captain Glover,sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.04,1:54:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么下来的\N{\fs55}How'd you get down,son?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.48,1:54:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,道斯送我下来的 豪威尔还在上面\N{\fs55}Doss. Howell's still up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.60,1:54:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,豪威尔和道斯做的吗\N{\fs55}What,Howell and Doss did this?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.12,1:54:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,主要是道斯\N{\fs55}Mostly just Doss.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.24,1:54:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 只是道斯吗 - 只是道斯\N{\fs55}- Just Doss? - Just Doss.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.12,1:54:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 胆小鬼道斯\N{\fs55}Yeah,Doss,the coward.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.68,1:56:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你就像是狗皮膏药 - 给我\N{\fs55}- You're like gum on a shoe,ain't you? - Give me this.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.00,1:56:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,现在练射击 有点晚了吧\N{\fs55}It's a bit late for target practice now,don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.64,1:56:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 上来 - 你开玩笑吧\N{\fs55}- Jump on it. - You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.68,1:56:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我拖你走\N{\fs55}No,I'm going to drag you.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.44,1:56:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那就来吧\N{\fs55}Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.28,1:56:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 准备好了吗 - 好了\N{\fs55}- Ready? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.60,1:56:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\fs55}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.56,1:56:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有追兵\N{\fs55}We got company.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.04,1:56:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\fs55}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.04,1:57:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,抬起手臂\N{\fs55}Arms up.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.92,1:57:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你在开玩笑吧 玉米秆\N{\fs55}You gotta be kidding me,Corn Stalk.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.56,1:57:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"你是在打单套结 不是编胸罩"\N{\fs55}"You're tying a bowline,boy, not building a bra."
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.84,1:57:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs55}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.12,1:57:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 准备好了吗 - 好了\N{\fs55}- Ready? - Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.40,1:57:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下去吧\N{\fs55}Get on.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.40,1:57:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 放我下来 - 是的 中士\N{\fs55}- Put me down! - Yes,Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.76,1:57:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 豪威尔中士 - 道斯还在上面\N{\fs55}- Sergeant Howell. - Doss is still up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.00,1:57:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么鬼 - 日本人还在追他\N{\fs55}- What the hell? - He's got Japs on his tail.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.32,1:58:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们接到他了\N{\fs55}We got him.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.64,1:58:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好样的\N{\fs55}That's good. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.52,1:58:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 接到他了\N{\fs55}It's okay,we got him.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:33.12,1:58:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没事了 道斯 - 没事的 道斯\N{\fs55}- It's okay,Doss. - Come on,Doss,come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.00,1:58:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你安全了\N{\fs55}You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.92,1:58:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,戴斯蒙 没事了\N{\fs55}Desmond,it's all right,it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:58.88,1:59:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,戴斯蒙\N{\fs55}Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:02.36,1:59:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,慢点 振作一些\N{\fs55}Easy,easy. Here,come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:11.28,1:59:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你受伤了吗\N{\fs55}Are you wounded?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.20,1:59:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs55}No. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.64,1:59:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,立即将这名战士送至医疗站\N{\fs55}Let's get this soldier to a hospital tent,right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:24.36,1:59:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来吧 轻点 - 慢一点\N{\fs55}- Come on,easy now. - Easy,easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.92,1:59:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,让开一下\N{\fs55}Make some space.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:11.44,2:00:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要人清理这里\N{\fs55}We need someone to come and clean up in here.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.08,2:00:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,欧文在哪\N{\fs55}Where's Irv?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:17.60,2:00:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你说医务兵谢克特吗 - 对的\N{\fs55}- Irv? You mean,Schecter the medic? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.48,2:00:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他没挺过来 休克死亡 血浆不够\N{\fs55}He didn't make it. He died of shock. No plasma.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:25.44,2:00:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs55}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.08,2:01:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为只是一个瘦小子 没看清你的本质\N{\fs55}All I saw was a skinny kid. I didn't know who you were.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:10.20,2:01:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你为国家做出的贡献\N{\fs55}You've done more than any other man could have done
Dialogue: 0,2:01:12.20,2:01:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,远超他人所及\N{\fs55}in the service of his country.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:14.64,2:01:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我一生中 从未如此看错人\N{\fs55}And I have never been more wrong about someone in my life.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:18.76,2:01:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,希望有一天 你能原谅我\N{\fs55}I hope one day you can forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:33.48,2:01:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们明天要重登钢锯岭\N{\fs55}We have to go back up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.32,2:01:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 明天是你的安息日\N{\fs55}I realize that tomorrow is your Sabbath.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.16,2:01:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这里大多数人 不理解你的信仰\N{\fs55}Most of these men don't believe the same way you do.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.56,2:01:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们都知道 你的信仰无比坚定\N{\fs55}But they believe so much in how much you believe.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.96,2:02:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你在钢锯岭的事迹 无疑是一个奇迹\N{\fs55}And what you did on that ridge, it's nothing short of a miracle,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:01.96,2:02:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也想见证奇迹\N{\fs55}and they want a piece of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:06.60,2:02:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有你一起 他们才能攀登上去\N{\fs55}And they're not going to go up there without you.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:20.00,2:02:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你究竟在等什么 上尉\N{\fs55}What the hell is your delay,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.80,2:02:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,十分钟前 就该发起进攻了\N{\fs55}You were supposed to begin that assault 10 minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:23.64,2:02:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们在等待 长官 - 等什么\N{\fs55}- We're waiting,sir. - Waiting for what?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:29.08,2:02:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,等列兵道斯完成祈祷 长官\N{\fs55}For Private Doss to finish praying for us,sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.00,2:02:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵道斯为你们祈祷吗\N{\fs55}Private Doss is praying for you?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:33.72,2:02:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是列兵道斯\N{\fs55}Who the hell is Private Doss?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:57.28,2:02:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\N{\fs55}Let's go to work.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:52.48,2:04:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下来\N{\fs55}Down. Get down!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:54.40,2:04:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,趴到地上 快点\N{\fs55}Get on the ground. On the ground. Now!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:37.40,2:05:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,躺下 我有吗啡\N{\fs55}Lay down,lay down. I got the morphine.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:41.00,2:05:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 带他们离开这里\N{\fs55}Let's go,let's get these men out of here.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:48.60,2:05:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我的圣经\N{\fs55}My Bible... My Bible. My Bible...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:52.76,2:05:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,停下 停下来\N{\fs55}Stop. Stop,stop,stop. Stop!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:55.60,2:05:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的圣经\N{\fs55}My Bible,my Bible,my Bible.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.04,2:06:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs55}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:15.48,2:07:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,戴斯蒙 你能回家了 我们拿下钢锯岭了\N{\fs55}You're going home,Desmond. We've taken Hacksaw.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:23.52,2:07:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 戴斯蒙\N{\fs55}Hold up,hold up! Desmond!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:27.84,2:07:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,戴斯蒙\N{\fs55}Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:43.37,2:08:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\bord0\shad0\\fs75\c&HE9E9E9&\pos(953.867,1019.455)}戴斯蒙德·道斯在钢锯岭救回75名伤员
Dialogue: 0,2:08:49.71,2:09:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\bord0\fs75\shad0\c&HE9E9E9&\pos(970.533,1046.92)}他是第一位获得荣誉勋章的拒服兵役者  这是表彰美国军人战斗精神的最高奖项
Dialogue: 0,2:09:03.35,2:09:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\bord0\fs75\shad0\c&HE9E9E9&\pos(970.533,1046.92)}戴斯蒙和桃乐茜结婚并相伴终生
Dialogue: 0,2:09:11.86,2:09:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\bord0\fs75\shad0\c&HE9E9E9&\pos(975.104,869.721)}尽管做出壮举 他依旧保持谦逊 将一切归功于信仰
Dialogue: 0,2:09:16.52,2:09:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在祈祷\N{\fs55}I was praying the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.12,2:09:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我祈祷着 主啊 请帮助我再救一人吧\N{\fs55}I just kept praying, "Lord,please help me get one more."
Dialogue: 0,2:09:24.44,2:09:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我救下一人后 继续祈祷 请帮助我再救一人吧\N{\fs55}When I got this,I said, "Lord,please help me get one more."
Dialogue: 0,2:09:29.42,2:09:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\bord0\fs75\shad0\c&HE9E9E9&\pos(967.104,888.052)}他曾说过 真正的英雄埋葬于此
Dialogue: 0,2:09:35.64,2:09:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,干预他人的信仰是错的\N{\fs55}I would say anyone is wrong
Dialogue: 0,2:09:38.16,2:09:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不论对方是谁\N{\fs55}to try to compromise somebody's conviction.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:40.20,2:09:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是军队 还是其他什么\N{\fs55}I don't care whether it's army or what it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.40,2:09:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,当你有信仰 那就不是玩笑\N{\fs55}When you own a conviction, that is not a joke.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:49.20,2:09:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你的全部\N{\fs55}That's what you are.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:52.32,2:09:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管我对他费尽口舌\N{\fs55}Even though I said those things to him
Dialogue: 0,2:09:54.68,2:09:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,让他带上步枪\N{\fs55}in regard to carrying a rifle,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:56.00,2:10:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,说他不带枪 跟我们就不是一伙人\N{\fs55}then he would never be by my damn side at all unless he had a rifle.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:02.68,2:10:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,直到后来\N{\fs55}But then,in the long run,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:05.64,2:10:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,发现他才是世上最勇敢的一个人\N{\fs55}finding out that he was one of the bravest persons alive.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:10.44,2:10:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,最后还是他救了我的命\N{\fs55}And then to have him end up saving my life
Dialogue: 0,2:10:13.28,2:10:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这简直太讽刺了\N{\fs55}was the irony of the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:16.52,2:10:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他的脸和眼睛沾满了血\N{\fs55}Blood had run down into the fella's face and eyes.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:21.84,2:10:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他躺在那 呻吟着呼唤医务兵\N{\fs55}He was laying there just groaning and calling for a medic.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:27.04,2:10:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒出水壶的水 拿出绷带 帮他洗脸\N{\fs55}I took water from my canteen, got some bandage,and I washed his face.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:34.16,2:10:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我洗净他的眼睛 他立刻睁大眼睛\N{\fs55}And when I... was washing his eyes, his eyes came open.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:39.08,2:10:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,兴奋到不行\N{\fs55}Man,he just lit up.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:43.88,2:10:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他说 我还以为自己瞎了\N{\fs55}He says,"I thought I was blind."
Dialogue: 0,2:10:47.88,2:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,整场战争 我收获的最好回报\N{\fs55}And if I hadn't got anything more out of the war
Dialogue: 0,2:10:51.04,2:10:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,就是他那一刻的笑容\N{\fs55}than that smile he gave me, I'd have been well repaid.
